(2, 1, '2013-12-03 09:44:23', '2013-12-03 09:44:23', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2013-12-03 11:17:09', '2013-12-03 11:17:09', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" width="1473">\r\n<h1>Welcome to Global-Migrate</h1>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Having been established by an immigration  expert who has many years of experience and has helped individuals, corporate clients, businessmen and high net worth investors with their immigration matters, we can proudly say that we are experts in most immigration matters. As one the most successful visa consultancies in the world we employ a wide range of consultants, immigration experts and highly qualified case workers. Our finest hour is always when we assist someone like you make their dream come true.Our aim is to provide our clients with the best service, before, during and after their visa process. Our high success rate is unrivaled, thus, making us the most trusted and reliable immigration consultants\r\n\r\nOur qualified experts are regulated by the Office of the Immigration Services Commissioner, Migration Agents regulatory Authority, Canadian Society of Immigration Consultants, and more making Global-Migrate a very special group of individuals.\r\nWe specialize in UK Visas and Immigration, Canadian Immigration Law, Emigration to Australia and Denmark Migration. Therefore, if you want to immigrate to any of these four destinations please get in touch with us.\r\n\r\nOver the past few years we have handled all types of immigration cases and enjoy a high success rate. Our organisational structure ensures a client is given a fast and efficient service that is second to none. Therefore, most of our clients state they would use us again or refer a friend or a family member.\r\n\r\nOur legally trained advisers fully understand that a visa application can be a very complex process therefore they are always keeping themselves up to date with the latest rules and regulations. We also have a very strong in house training program which allows our staff to have the latest knowledge of any immigration process so that they can help you lodge strong applications.\r\n\r\nWhether you need a visa for the UK, immigration to Australia, a Green Card for Denmark or a Canadian Skilled Visa just call us for a FREE assessment to see if you are eligible. We offer tailored made packages and detailed immigration advice, aiming to give everyone who contacts us a detailed assessment of their case so we can develop an understanding of their immigration requirements.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>How to get the process started?</h4>\r\nBecause our clients are important to us, the starting point of our relationship is an immigration evaluation, which is FREE. We will only take on a case if we believe that we can help submit a strong application for you, thus increasing the chances of success. As we make several applications every month, in some circumstances we can prejudge what the outcome "could" be.\r\n\r\nThis way you save your time and get great value for your money.This is one reason why most of the clients who contact us feel confident in using our service as they do not want a refusal of their application.\r\n\r\nWe offer an efficient and reliable service with affordable prices. We have a dedicated team of advisors who are always available on the other end of the phone for you. On many occasions our staff works extra hours, if required, to help our client. The best part is that they don’t do this for financial gains, they do it for the satisfaction of the client.\r\n\r\nThinking of migrating? Why don''t you call and speak to our highly knowledgeable consultants on 0203 589 6791</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</t