 always answered all my questions even though sometimes I used to bug him by calling him 2 times every day. Thank you Fayyaz for being patient and helping me secure my visa.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. Jayanathan Radhakrishnan, London, UK – 2012:</strong> <em>Thank you sir for assisting with my Green Card visa for Denmark. I am very happy to use your services.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. Matthew Johnson, Leeds, UK – 2012:</strong> <em>I applied for my working holiday visa for Australia through this company and got my visa in 48 hours. I will gladly recommend them to my friends and family.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. Christopher James, Crawley, UK – 2011:</strong> <em>I used the services of Global-Migrate for my marriage visa for Australia. I had just got married to my long time partner who is an Australian Citizen. I was very scared at the beginning as I did not want my visa to be rejected. I spoke to many consultants who, by the sound of it, were only interested in my money. When I spoke to Adam at Global-Migrate he spent time explaining the benefits and advantaged of using their company. I was very happy to find out that they hired a MARA agent. I was so impressed by the time and effort Adam made to make sure I understood the enitre visa process in detail that I did not hesitate to use their services and I can now say that I did not make the wrong decision. I was kept up to date with my application process and at not at any point did it seem to me that I was wasting my money. I would specially like to thank Adam and his team for giving me the confidence in using Global-Migrate.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Miss Sandra Allan, Sussex, UK – 2011:</strong> <em>Global-Migrate helped me apply for a course of my choice in a recognised institue in Canada and also helped me with the study visa process. It took them only 12 weeks to complete the whole process and I am flying to Canada next week.</em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Richard Lee Roy, Manchester, UK – 2011:</strong> <em>In all honesty I cannot think of one negative thing I can add on this testimonial. Me and my partner had been thinking of migrating to Canada for quite some time and were looking for a professional organisation to assist us with this application. When we spoke to Global-Migrate for the first time, they arranged a face-to-face consultation with one of there very experienced Canadian case worker. We had a free initial consultation which lasted approximately 40 minutes and we were so impressed by the professionalism of the case worker that we had to hire them immediately. The entire application took almost a year to be granted and we were so satisfied with the assistance we received that we have recommended at least 3 other family members to Global-Migrate ever since. Highly recommended.</em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Ahmed W Bhatti, Lahore, Pakistan – 2011:</strong> <em>It was a hard decision to use someone who was based in another country, but after speaking to Global-Migrate consultants I was very satisfied and confident that my application will be in safe hands. I received my Tier 4 Visa within 3 weeks. </em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Manish Agarwal, London, UK – 2011:</strong> <em>Global-Migrate was the only company who offered me a very decent fee for my application. My Tier 1 General application was a bit complex as I was claiming income through self employment and employment. I spoke to many company who were quoting me very high fees due to the complexity of my case. Global-Migrate consultants were very helpful throughout the case. Once I had paid them my fee there customer service was even better and that showed that they were not interested in my money only. My application was successful and I thank Global-Migrate for being so helpful. </em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Miss Samantha Collins, Toronto, Canada – 2011:</strong> <em>I applied for an Australian Skilled Visa through Global-Migrate. I was very skeptical with which consultant I would use for my visa as Australian Immigration was a very lenghty and costly process. There are many bogus consultants out there who charge thousands of pounds but never produce any result. It took me 2 weeks to make a decision but in the end I went with Global-Migrate as their team came across very professional, they have a MARA regsitered agent in their team and the fee they were charging me was not as high as many other agents out there. They assisted me throughout the entire process and in about 16 months my application was approved. I am not planning on moving to Australia ASAP. I am glad I chose Global-Migrate in the end. </em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mrs. Mandisa Abrahams, Buffalo City, South Africa - 2011:</strong> <em>My Grand parents were born in the UK and I knew I could apply for a UK Ancestry visa so I contacted Global-Migrate because I saw on there Website that they worked on a No Visa No fee policy. I did come across other companies in South Africa who claimed that they were big and well renowned but once I searched on the Internet they did not have many positive reviews so I decided to use Global-Migrate and do not regret using there service. Brilliant customer services and assistance with my application. I will be flying to the UK with my UK Ancestry Visa in 4 days. Thank you Global-Migrate for making my dream come true. </em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Abayomiolorunkoje ABASIEKEME, London, UK – 2010:</strong><em> Brilliant service. Always answered my questions on time. Good communication from them at all times and very professional. God bless.</em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Mr. Sanjeeva Sampath Chandana, Southampton, UK – 2010:</strong> <em>I am very happy with Global-Migrate services. Very helpful and efficient. I will definitely recommend to my friends. My initial application was refused as I applied myself. The UKBA gave me 7 days to re-submit my application and Global-Migrate were able to do so for me and secure a successful application too. What more could I have asked for. </em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Vijay Anand, Reading, UK – 2010: </strong><em>Thank you Global-Migrate for helping me with my British Citizenship application. </em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:38', '2014-11-14 16:20:38', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
