ompanies in South Africa who claimed that they were big and well renowned but once I searched on the Internet they did not have many positive reviews so I decided to use Global-Migrate and do not regret using there service. Brilliant customer services and assistance with my application. I will be flying to the UK with my UK Ancestry Visa in 4 days. Thank you Global-Migrate for making my dream come true. </em></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Abayomiolorunkoje ABASIEKEME, London, UK &#8211; 2008:</strong><em> Brilliant service. Always answered my questions on time. Good communication from them at all times and very professional. God bless.</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mr. Sanjeeva Sampath Chandana, Southampton, UK &#8211; 2007:</strong> <em>I am very happy with Global-Migrate services. Very helpful and efficient. I will definitely recommend to my friends. My initial application was refused as I applied myself. The UKBA gave me 7 days to re-submit my application and Global-Migrate were able to do so for me and secure a successful application too. What more could I have asked for. </em></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Mr. Vijay Anand, Reading, UK &#8211; 2006: </strong><em>Thank you Global-Migrate for helping me with my British Citizenship application. </em></p>\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a href="free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n    