(25, 1, '2013-12-03 13:11:58', '2013-12-03 13:11:58', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">\r\n<h4>The Office of the Immigration Services Commissioner (OISC)</h4>\r\nOISC is an independent public body set up under the Immigration and Asylum Act 1999. It is responsible for regulating immigration advisers in accordance with the Commissioner''s Code of Standards and Rules. It is responsible for regulating immigration advisers in accordance with the Commissioner''s Code of Standards and Rules. Global-Migrate is registered with the OISC, giving all our clients peace of mind, confidence and above all protection with their case and money. Our registration number is F201100270\r\n<h4>Immigration Consultants of Canada Regulatory Council (ICCRC).</h4>\r\nGlobal-Migrate hires a team of experienced Canadian immigration case workers therefore giving you the peace of mind that your application is dealt with and handled by an authorised person who has the experience and expertise to work with you towards a successful application.\r\n<h4>Migration Agents Registration Authority (MARA)</h4>\r\nGlobal-Migrate uses the services of a Independent Contracting Registered Migration Agent which means that a MARA registered agent will handle your case, if required. Normally your case is dealt by an experienced Australian Immigration caseworker who works from our office in London. This gives all our clients the peace of mind that their Australian application is being dealt with by an experienced caseworker.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Accreditations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a