(47, 1, '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\nSkilled Immigration to Australia is the most common and popular route for highly skilled people. Australia has a history of employing high quality skilled workers, especially from countries like the UK. All skilled workers get rewarded in the form of high salaries, career growth and stability. Workers from different kind of trades, including Carpenters, Plumbers, Welders, Floor tilers, Mechanics, Electricians, IT consultants, Teachers, Accountants migrate to Australia every day, every week, every month. Global Migrate is proud to be a part of their journey.<br><br>\r\nThe three options available for Skilled Immigration to Australia are;\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Skilled Independent Visa - (Subclass 189)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Independent visa is a points-based application. To qualify for the independent visa, you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements, you will be eligible for this visa. This visa is without a doubt the most desired route of immigration to Australia; however, you need to score very high points to be able to apply for this visa. This is an independent application which means no state, or territory will sponsor you and you need to score the required points without having to claim any bonus points for sponsorship.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-189.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated Visa &ndash; (Subclass 190)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Sponsored visa is a points-based application. To qualify for this type of visa you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements you may be eligible for this visa. Once approved you become a permanent resident of Australia from day one however you have a restriction to your stay in Australia, where you need to live in the region that sponsors your occupation for at least 24 months.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-190.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Visa &ndash; (Subclass 489) </h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Regional Sponsored visa is initially based on meeting a point score. To qualify for this visa, you must first pass basic requirements. You get points for your age, English competence, training, work experience and having an eligible relative (or a state) able to sponsor you. Once you meet these requirements, you may be eligible for this type of visa. This is initially a 3 year visa sponsored by a state.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-489.html">Read More… </a></strong></p>\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n       ', 'Skilled Immigration Australia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'skilled-immigration-australia', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=47', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(48, 1, '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '<div id="body-contentpanle">\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\nSkilled Immigration to Australia is the most common and popular route for highly skilled people. Australia has a history of employing high quality skilled workers, especially from countries like the UK. All skilled workers get rewarded in the form of high salaries, career growth and stability. Workers from different kind of trades, including Carpenters, Plumbers, Welders, Floor tilers, Mechanics, Electricians, IT consultants, Teachers, Accountants migrate to Australia every day, every week, every month. Global Migrate is proud to be a part of their journey.<br><br>\r\nThe three options available for Skilled Immigration to Australia are;\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Skilled Independent Visa - (Subclass 189)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Independent visa is a points-based application. To qualify for the independent visa, you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements, you will be eligible for this visa. This visa is without a doubt the most desired route of immigration to Australia; however, you need to score very high points to be able to apply for this visa. This is an independent application which means no state, or territory will sponsor you and you need to score the required points without having to claim any bonus points for sponsorship.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-189.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated Visa &ndash; (Subclass 190)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Sponsored visa is a points-based application. To qualify for this type of visa you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements you may be eligible for this visa. Once approved you become a permanent resident of Australia from day one however you have a restriction to your stay in Australia, where you need to live in the region that sponsors your occupation for at least 24 months.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-190.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Visa &ndash; (Subclass 489) </h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Regional Sponsored visa is initially based on meeting a point score. To qualify for this visa, you must first pass basic requirements. You get points for your age, English competence, training, work experience and having an eligible relative (or a state) able to sponsor you. Once you meet these requirements, you may be eligible for this type of visa. This is initially a 3 year visa sponsored by a state.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-489.html">Read More… </a></strong></p>\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>', 'Skilled Immigration Australia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '2013-12-05 11:40:44', '', 47, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=48', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2013-12-05 11:42:49', '2013-12-05 11:42:49', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Australia offers a set of points-based visas for skilled workers from around the world. These visas allow you to migrate to Australia and can give you permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Independent Visa, also known as Subclass 189.If you’re considering a move to Australia, a Skilled Independent Visa might be right for you. To get your free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\nThe Skilled Independent Visa has some basic requirements, including an English language requirement and an age limit of 50 years old. To apply for the visa, you will need to submit an expression of interest, in which you provide information about your occupation.\r\n<a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> </a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAustralia’s Skilled Occupation List includes details of the types of occupations that are eligible for the subclass 189 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine if your occupation is included in the list. You will also need to have a skill assessment to determine if your skills within that occupation are suitable.\r\n\r\nAlthough you will need to prove your ability, the Subclass 189 visa can be a great opportunity for you to live and work in Australia. To find out about the requirements for a particular occupation, and to find out how to maximise your chances of getting approved for this type of visa, call Global-Migrate’s MARA regulated advisors.\r\n\r\nOnce your expression of interest is approved, you’ll be invited to apply for the Skilled Independent Visa. The visa can allow you, and a spouse, to travel freely to Australia for up to five years. If you are interested in applying for this visa, get in touch with us today.\r\n\r\nWith years of skilled migration experience, Global-Migrate’s consultants are able to help you find the best path for your migration. We offer a free initial assessment that can tell you whether you can qualify for a Subclass 189 visa, so call or email today.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n\r\n<div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Skilled Independent Subclass 189 Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'skilled-independent-subclass-189-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '2014-11-14 16:20:24', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=49', 0, 'page', '', 0),
