(55, 1, '2013-12-05 11:45:48', '2013-12-05 11:45:48', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n               The Partner Visa is a way for people married to Australian citizens and permanent residents, as well as eligible New Zealand citizens, to live in Australia. When you are granted a partner visa, you will be able to live, work, and study in Australia.<br><br>\r\nIf you are considering applying for a partner visa, call Global-migrate for a free visa assessment. We have a 100% success rate for partner visa applications, and can offer advice on your application. Our advisors are highly trained immigration professionals. We also offer a ‘no visa, no fee’ policy, and guarantee that we can help our clients submit a strong application.<br><br>\r\nFor a partner visa, you will need to provide evidence of your relationship. This needs to be show in a variety of ways, and many people who apply without the assistance of an immigration professional fail to show sufficient evidence. We can help you figure out what you need to include, and can help you as you write your personal history statement.<br><br>\r\nYou will also need to meet certain character and legal requirements. These are fairly straightforward, but can get confusing. If you have any questions about what else might be required of you for this type of visa, Global-Migrate can help.<br><br>\r\nWhen you are granted your partner visa, you will generally be given a temporary visa while a decision is made on your permanent visa. Your permanent visa will allow you to live, work, and study in Australia permanently. It will also allow you to earn certain benefits, and will allow you to apply for Australian citizenship after you have met certain criteria.<br><br>\r\nIf you are planning on moving to Australia with your partner, Global-Migrate’s advisors can help answer any questions you might have. Give us a call today to get a free visa assessment.\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n', 'Australia Partner or "Spouse" Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'australia-partner-or-spouse-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:19:50', '2014-11-14 16:19:50', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=55', 0, 'page', '', 0),
