(60, 1, '2013-12-05 11:47:39', '2013-12-05 11:47:39', '<div id="body-contentpanle">\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                  Australian Visa under the Study Visa category is for applicants who plan to go to Australia for higher education. At Global-Migrate we hire a dedicated team of MARA regulated consultants to advise those who might be interested in migrating to Australia to study. As we have been in business for over 15 years and work with all established education institutions in Australia we are in a postion to help you secure a place at the University, School or College of your choice. We are so confident of securing this visa for you that we offer you a No Visa No Fee policy for this application.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nAustralia has a reputation for having some of the world’s leading education institutions. By Joining the thousands of satisfied international students studying in Australia, you will experience a unique kind of education.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFirst and foremost you will need to be enrolled by a recognised university in Australia, which we can help you with. Once you have an acceptance letter you would be able to make an application for a study visa provided you have enough finances to cover your tuition fee and your cost of living for the entire period of your stay.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nWe also provide a complete relocation service from Airport transfers to finding an accomodation and opening bank accounts to name a few\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYour student visa will list the conditions that apply specifically to you. It is important to comply with your visa conditions to avoid visa cancellation.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThere many different types of study visas available.\r\n\r\n</p><h4>How to apply</h4>\r\nTo find out more please contac