(83, 1, '2013-12-05 12:17:40', '2013-12-05 12:17:40', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                Moving to Australia can be a great decision. It is a beautiful country, and one that has many draws for people all over the world. If you’re planning a move to Australia, you’ll want to speak to one of Global-Migrate’s qualified immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nYour reasons for moving to Australia will determine which type of visa you need. Some visas are intended for family members of Australian nationals, while others are for those who are going to Australia for work purposes. To find out which visa is right for you, start your free visa assessment now.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re looking to move to Australia for work, you might be able to get a visa on the basis of your work experience and training. You can also get an employer to sponsor your visa application. For people aged between 18 and 30, it is also possible to apply for the very popular working holiday visa.<br><br>\r\nIf you have family members who are Australian nationals, you might be eligible to join them. In this case, you would need to apply for a special family visa, or a partner visa.<br><br>\r\nWith so many types of visa available, it can be difficult for you to know which is right for you.Our agents can help you through the complex and stressful visa process. They are trained immigration advisors, and are experts at helping people through this life-changing event. <br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate hires agents who are registered with the Migration Agents Registration Authority (MARA). This provides our clients with the best possible service for all their Australian immigration needs. <br><br>\r\nWith fifteen years of experience helping people make their immigration dreams come true, we are one of the world’s largest and most successful immigration consultancies. If you’re considering a move to Australia, call us today for a free visa assessment.<br><br>\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        ', 'Australia Visa and Immigration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:17:40', '2013-12-05 12:17:40', '', 43, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=83', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(84, 1, '2013-12-05 12:18:22', '2013-12-05 12:18:22', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                For some types of Australian visa, you will first need to submit an expression of interest. This preliminary application is not the same as the visa application itself. If your Expression of Interest is successful, you will be given an invitation to apply for the relevant visa.\r\nMuch like a visa application, though, the Expression of Interest can be a confusing and complex process. To get advice and a free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nAn Expression of Interest is required for many skilled worker visas. In your EOI, you will be providing information about your qualifications and experience. This will help Australian immigration determine if you meet the requirements for the program you are interested in.<br><br>\r\nTo file an Expression of Interest, you won’t need to submitting supporting documents. However, if you are invited to apply for a visa, you will need these. Any information you include in your EOI will have to be backed up when it comes time to apply for your visa. Global-Migrate’s consultants can help you prepare for your EOI and visa submission/\r\nSubmitting an incorrect EOI can leave you without an invitation to apply for a visa. This is why it is crucial your EOI is correct, and that you submit it for the right type of visa.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s team of MARA registered consultants can help make sure your Expression of Interest will be successful. We know what is required for each visa program, so can save you the time and hassle of an unsuccessful submission.<br><br>\r\nAt Global-Migrate, we only take on cases that we believe will be successful. Our free initial assessment will help you determine if a skilled migrant visa is right for you. Many people share your dream of working in Australia, and the EOI is the first step to making that dream a reality. <br><br>\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n  ', 'Expression of Interest - EOI', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:18:22', '2013-12-05 12:18:22', '', 45, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=84', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(85, 1, '2013-12-05 12:18:47', '2013-12-05 12:18:47', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\nSkilled Immigration to Australia is the most common and popular route for highly skilled people. Australia has a history of employing high quality skilled workers, especially from countries like the UK. All skilled workers get rewarded in the form of high salaries, career growth and stability. Workers from different kind of trades, including Carpenters, Plumbers, Welders, Floor tilers, Mechanics, Electricians, IT consultants, Teachers, Accountants migrate to Australia every day, every week, every month. Global Migrate is proud to be a part of their journey.<br><br>\r\nThe three options available for Skilled Immigration to Australia are;\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Skilled Independent Visa - (Subclass 189)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Independent visa is a points-based application. To qualify for the independent visa, you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements, you will be eligible for this visa. This visa is without a doubt the most desired route of immigration to Australia; however, you need to score very high points to be able to apply for this visa. This is an independent application which means no state, or territory will sponsor you and you need to score the required points without having to claim any bonus points for sponsorship.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-189.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated Visa &ndash; (Subclass 190)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Sponsored visa is a points-based application. To qualify for this type of visa you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements you may be eligible for this visa. Once approved you become a permanent resident of Australia from day one however you have a restriction to your stay in Australia, where you need to live in the region that sponsors your occupation for at least 24 months.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-190.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Visa &ndash; (Subclass 489) </h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Regional Sponsored visa is initially based on meeting a point score. To qualify for this visa, you must first pass basic requirements. You get points for your age, English competence, training, work experience and having an eligible relative (or a state) able to sponsor you. Once you meet these requirements, you may be eligible for this type of visa. This is initially a 3 year visa sponsored by a state.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-489.html">Read More… </a></strong></p>\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n       ', 'Skilled Immigration Australia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:18:47', '2013-12-05 12:18:47', '', 47, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=85', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(86, 1, '2013-12-05 12:19:16', '2013-12-05 12:19:16', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n               \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                Australia offers a set of points-based visas for skilled workers from around the world. These visas allow you to migrate to Australia and can give you permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Independent Visa, also known as Subclass 189.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re considering a move to Australia, a Skilled Independent Visa might be right for you. To get your free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nThe Skilled Independent Visa has some basic requirements, including an English language requirement and an age limit of 50 years old. To apply for the visa, you will need to submit an expression of interest, in which you provide information about your occupation.<br>\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"></a></p><div class="more"></div>\r\n<br>\r\nAustralia’s Skilled Occupation List includes details of the types of occupations that are eligible for the subclass 189 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine if your occupation is included in the list. You will also need to have a skill assessment to determine if your skills within that occupation are suitable.<br><br>\r\nAlthough you will need to prove your ability, the Subclass 189 visa can be a great opportunity for you to live and work in Australia. To find out about the requirements for a particular occupation, and to find out how to maximise your chances of getting approved for this type of visa, call Global-Migrate’s MARA regulated advisors.<br><br>\r\nOnce your expression of interest is approved, you’ll be invited to apply for the Skilled Independent Visa. The visa can allow you, and a spouse, to travel freely to Australia for up to five years. If you are interested in applying for this visa, get in touch with us today.<br><br>\r\nWith years of skilled migration experience, Global-Migrate’s consultants are able to help you find the best path for your migration. We offer a free initial assessment that can tell you whether you can qualify for a Subclass 189 visa, so call or email today.\r\n\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n  ', 'Skilled Independent Subclass 189 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '49-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:19:16', '2013-12-05 12:19:16', '', 49, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=86', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(87, 1, '2013-12-05 12:19:58', '2013-12-05 12:19:58', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n               Australia has long been a popular immigration destination. The country’s points-based visa system allows certain skilled workers to gain permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Nominated, or subclass 190, Visa.<br><br>\r\nIf you are thinking of applying for a Skilled Nominated Visa, get in touch with Global-Migrate today for a free visa assessment. Our qualified advisors can help determine if this is the right visa for you.<br><br>\r\nAs with all of Australia’s skilled worker visas, the subclass 190 visa does have some basic requirements. These include an English language requirement as well as an age requirement. If you’re under 50 and have the language ability, you can submit an expression of interest for a subclass 190 visa.<br>\r\n <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> </a></p><div class="more"></div>\r\n <br>\r\nLike the other skilled worker visas, you will need to pass the points assessment for the Skilled Nominated visa. To find out about what can earn you points, and how many points you’ll need, speak to Global-Migrate’s MARA registered consultants. We have helped many people with their skilled immigration applications, and can help you with yours.<br><br>\r\nFor the Skilled Nominated visa, you will also need a state or territory nomination. Some states and territories are in need of specific types of skilled workers. If you receive a nomination, you will need to settle in that state or territory. If you want to find out about the benefits, and limits, of a nomination speak to a Global-Migrate representative today.<br><br>\r\nThe subclass 190 visa can be a great way to migrate to Australia. If you qualify, it can give you and your spouse the ability to take up permanent residency in Australia, and can put you on the path to citizenship.<br><br>\r\nOf course, as with any visa application, the Australian subclass 190 visa process can be confusing. Working with an experienced immigration advisor like global-Migrate can help ensure you’re submitting your application correctly. Call us, or request a call back, today.\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n     ', 'Skilled &ndash; Nominated (subclass 190) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:19:58', '2013-12-05 12:19:58', '', 51, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=87', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(88, 1, '2013-12-05 12:20:10', '2013-12-05 12:20:10', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                Australia offers skilled workers permanent residency under the points-based visa system. One of these visa types is the Skilled Regional Sponsored, or subclass 489, visa. Like the other visas in this system, you must demonstrate knowledge of the English language, and you must be under 50 years old.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s MARA regulated immigration advisors have helped many people with their skilled migrant visas. To receive your free visa assessment, get in touch today. We can help determine in the subclass 489 visa is right for you.<br><br>\r\nTo qualify for this visa, you must also have sponsorship from a relative in Australia. The Skilled Regional visa is aimed at certain Designated Areas of Australia. Your family member must live in one of these areas. To find out what relatives can sponsor you, and where they must live, get in touch with Global-Migrate for the most up-to-date information.<br>\r\n <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> </a></p><div class="more"></div>\r\n <br>\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you can apply on the basis of a nomination from a participating state or territory government. For more information about this path, and how to get a nomination, call Global-Migrate’s advisors today.<br><br>\r\nOur consultants can also give you guidance about the application process. For the subclass 489 visa, you will need to first submit an expression of interest, in which you will need to give information about your occupation and your skill level. Global-Migrate can help you with your Expression of Interest, and can help you find out about what occupations are in demand in Australia.<br><br>\r\nThe 489 visa can be a great option for living and working in Australia. While you will need to stay in the specific area of your sponsorship or nomination during the first part of your visa, you will be eligible to apply for permanent residency after two years. When this is granted, you will be free to live and work in any part of Australia.<br><br>\r\nThe Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Provisional Visa can be the ideal way for you to migrate to Australia. To find out more about this and other visas, and to find out the best choice for you, call Global-Migrate’s experienced advisors today.\r\n\r\n\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        ', 'Skilled-Nominated or Sponsored (Provisional)-(subclass 489) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '53-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:20:10', '2013-12-05 12:20:10', '', 53, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=88', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2013-12-05 12:20:29', '2013-12-05 12:20:29', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n               The Partner Visa is a way for people married to Australian citizens and permanent residents, as well as eligible New Zealand citizens, to live in Australia. When you are granted a partner visa, you will be able to live, work, and study in Australia.<br><br>\r\nIf you are considering applying for a partner visa, call Global-migrate for a free visa assessment. We have a 100% success rate for partner visa applications, and can offer advice on your application. Our advisors are highly trained immigration professionals. We also offer a ‘no visa, no fee’ policy, and guarantee that we can help our clients submit a strong application.<br><br>\r\nFor a partner visa, you will need to provide evidence of your relationship. This needs to be show in a variety of ways, and many people who apply without the assistance of an immigration professional fail to show sufficient evidence. We can help you figure out what you need to include, and can help you as you write your personal history statement.<br><br>\r\nYou will also need to meet certain character and legal requirements. These are fairly straightforward, but can get confusing. If you have any questions about what else might be required of you for this type of visa, Global-Migrate can help.<br><br>\r\nWhen you are granted your partner visa, you will generally be given a temporary visa while a decision is made on your permanent visa. Your permanent visa will allow you to live, work, and study in Australia permanently. It will also allow you to earn certain benefits, and will allow you to apply for Australian citizenship after you have met certain criteria.<br><br>\r\nIf you are planning on moving to Australia with your partner, Global-Migrate’s advisors can help answer any questions you might have. Give us a call today to get a free visa assessment.\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n', 'Australia Partner or "Spouse" Visa ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '55-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:20:29', '2013-12-05 12:20:29', '', 55, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=89', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(90, 1, '2013-12-05 12:20:47', '2013-12-05 12:20:47', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                 \r\nIf you’re the family member of an Australian citizen or permanent resident, you can join them in Australia on a family visa. Family members of eligible New Zealand citizens can also migrate to Australia on one of these popular visas.<br><br>\r\nYour relationship will determine which visa is right for you. If you’re not sure which visa you should apply for, get in touch with us today for your free visa assessment with Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors. We are the UK’s largest and most trusted Australian immigration consultancies, and can help you determine your immigration options.\r\n</p><h4>Partner (Spouse) Visas</h4>\r\nFor Australian immigration, partners include fiancés, married partners, and de facto partners, including those in same-sex relationship. A partner visa will allow you to enter and/or gain permanent residency in Australia. To find out if you are eligible for this type of visa, call our MARA certified consultants.\r\n<h4>Parent Visas</h4>\r\nIf you are the parent of an Australian citizen or permanent resident, or eligible New Zealand citizen, you can apply for a parent visa. This type of visa can give you permanent residency in Australia. If you want more details about how you or your parents can migrate to Australia, get in touch with us today to discuss visa options.\r\n\r\n<h4>Child Visas</h4>\r\nChildren of Australian citizens and permanent residents, and eligible New Zealand citizens, can also travel to and reside permanently in Australia. Child visas are available for dependent children, orphan relatives, and adopted children. Our visa advisors can help you apply for this type of visa, so get in touch today.<br><br>\r\nOther family visas are also available, including visas for aged dependent relatives, carers, and remaining relatives. If you are considering making a family visa application, speak to our trained and qualified advisors for up-to-date information, and a free visa assessment.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s immigration consultants are MARA certified, and can help you determine the right visa for your individual case.\r\n\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n   ', 'Australia Family Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '57-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:20:47', '2013-12-05 12:20:47', '', 57, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=90', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2013-12-05 12:21:16', '2013-12-05 12:21:16', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                  Australian Visa under the Study Visa category is for applicants who plan to go to Australia for higher education. At Global-Migrate we hire a dedicated team of MARA regulated consultants to advise those who might be interested in migrating to Australia to study. As we have been in business for over 15 years and work with all established education institutions in Australia we are in a postion to help you secure a place at the University, School or College of your choice. We are so confident of securing this visa for you that we offer you a No Visa No Fee policy for this application.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nAustralia has a reputation for having some of the world’s leading education institutions. By Joining the thousands of satisfied international students studying in Australia, you will experience a unique kind of education.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFirst and foremost you will need to be enrolled by a recognised university in Australia, which we can help you with. Once you have an acceptance letter you would be able to make an application for a study visa provided you have enough finances to cover your tuition fee and your cost of living for the entire period of your stay.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nWe also provide a complete relocation service from Airport transfers to finding an accomodation and opening bank accounts to name a few\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYour student visa will list the conditions that apply specifically to you. It is important to comply with your visa conditions to avoid visa cancellation.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThere many different types of study visas available.\r\n\r\n</p><h4>How to apply</h4>\r\nTo find out more please contact our Australian team on +44 (0)207 9934762 or use our free assessment tool below\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n', 'Australia Study Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '59-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:21:16', '2013-12-05 12:21:16', '', 59, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=91', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(92, 1, '2013-12-05 12:21:33', '2013-12-05 12:21:33', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                  </p><h4>Business Owner (Provisional) (Subclass 160)</h4>\r\nThis visa is suitable for successful business men or women, who have a successful business career, and have a genuine and realistic commitment to be involved as an owner in a new or existing business in Australia. This visa is also the first step towards being granted a permanent Business Skills visa.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThis visa is for business owners from overseas who intend to own a business in Australia, and are less than 45 years of age.\r\n\r\n<h4>State/Territory Sponsored Business Owner (Provisional) (Subclass 163)</h4>\r\nThis visa is suitable for successful business men or women, who have a genuine and realistic commitment to be involved as an owner in a new or existing business in Australia. This visa is also the first step towards being granted a permanent Business Skills visa.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThis visa is for business owners from overseas who intend to own a business in Australia, and are less than 55 years old. You\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nAll classes of business visa for investors / senior executives and business men wanting to trade and establish a business in will need assets of at least AUD $ 500 000, speak English and have a good business background.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nSenior executive visas are available for management of high profile profitable corporations.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nInvestor visas are available for applicants with large sums of money to invest in Australia in fixed funds.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFor more information on any of the above visas or to find out if you qualify for one, please call +44 (0)207 9934762\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        \r\n', 'Australia Business Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:21:33', '2013-12-05 12:21:33', '', 61, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=92', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(93, 1, '2013-12-05 12:21:56', '2013-12-05 12:21:56', '\r\n            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                  A tourist visa is one of the most popular visas for Australia. There are many categories of visitors. A visitor is someone who generally intends to be in Australia for a short period, for example, to visit friends and family, to do business, to do a short course of study, to have private medical treatment. The information given here aims to deal with the various categories of visitors coming to Australia.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIn general, you must show that:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n<li> you want to visit Australia for no more than six months;</li>\r\n<li> you intend to leave at the end of your visit;</li>\r\n<li>you have enough money to support yourself during your stay</li>\r\n<li> you do not intend to take paid or unpaid employment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe different types of tourist visas for Australia are:\r\n<h4>ETA (Visitor) (Subclass 976)</h4>\r\nAn electronically stored authority for short-term visits to Australia of up to 3 months. Available to passport holders from a number of countries and regions, who are outside Australia.\r\n\r\n<h4>eVisitors (Subclass 651)</h4>\r\nAn electronically stored authority for visits to Australia for tourism or business purposes for up to three months. Available to passport holders from the European Union and a number of other European countries, who are outside Australia.\r\n\r\n<h4>Tourist visa (Subclass 676)</h4>\r\nA temporary visa allowing a stay in Australia of up to three or six or 12 months. Applicants can apply from both outside and in Australia. Some tourists are eligible to lodge an online application for an e676 Tourist visa.\r\n\r\n<h4>Sponsored Family Visitor visa (Subclass 679)</h4>\r\nFor people seeking to visit family in Australia for a stay period of up to 12 months. Formal sponsorship by an Australian citizen or permanent resident is required.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nTo find out more or to apply for a successful tourist visa for Australia please call us on +44 (0) 207 9934762\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n', 'Australia Tourist Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:21:56', '2013-12-05 12:21:56', '', 63, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=93', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
