(103, 1, '2013-12-05 12:25:29', '2013-12-05 12:25:29', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">The Federal Skilled Worker Visa is a popular way of getting permanent residency in Canada. The points-based program allows those who meet certain criteria to become permanent residents. Global-Migrate has helped thousands of people immigrate to Canada over the years. If you are interested in applying for a Canadian visa, call us today for your free immigration assessment.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Federal Skilled Worker Visa will be accepting new applications from May 2014. Although there will be limited availability for this application. Depending on your occupation you may qualify for this visa. To find out more please get in touch with our Canadian department. When it reopens to new applications, it will use a new points table. Global-Migrate’s immigration advisors can help you plan for an application using the new criteria.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe changing rules for the Federal Skilled Worker Program will still include a many of the same requirements. These include education, language proficiency, work experience, age, whether you have arranged employment, and your adaptability. You will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself when you get to Canada.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo make sure your application is successful, you’ll need to use the most up to date visa information. Global-Migrate’s expert advisors are on top of all changes to Canadian visa rules, and can help figure out the right category for you. Before you apply on your own, get in touch for a free visa assessment and find out how we can help you.\r\n\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate has a very high success rate for Canadian visa applications, and can help ensure that your visa application is not rejected. Whatever stage you’re at in your visa application, our ICCRC visa experts can provide assistance.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe benefits of a Federal Skilled 