(107, 1, '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Over a 100,000 students go to study in Canada every year and even more come to Canada to learn English or French.Before you can apply for a study permit, you must have been accepted at a recognized school, university or college in Canada. You must also show evidence that you can financially support yourself.\r\n\r\nYou will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself during your studies. This is calculated using system. The total amount you must be able to show will vary depending on the place and type of study you are undertaking.\r\n\r\nTo get a clear understanding of how much you will need, and how you will need to prove it, contact Global Migrate''s trained advisors.\r\n\r\nOnce you enter Canada you must also prove that you are a Law-abiding citizen in the country of your residence and do not hold any criminal record. The Canadian government may ask you to provide a police certificate. You must be of sound health and if required will be happy to take a medical test. Last but by no means least you must be able to satisfy an immigration officer that you intend to leave Canada at the end of your education.\r\n\r\nGlobal Migrate also has a specialist team which works directly with recognised Universities and Colleges in Canada to secure an offer of study for you.\r\n\r\nPlease speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit\r\n<a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn some cases, you do not require a study permit to go to school in Canada.\r\n\r\nIf you wish to study in a short-term course or program\r\n\r\nYou do not need a study permit if you plan to take a course or program in Canada that lasts six months or less. You must complete the course or program within the period authorized for your stay in Canada\r\n<h4>Foreign representatives to Canada</h4>\r\nIf you are a family member or staff member of a foreign representative to Canada accredited by Foreign Affairs and International Trade Canada, you may not need a permit to study in Canada.\r\n<h4>Members of foreign armed forces</h4>\r\nIf you are a member of a foreign armed force under the Visiting Forces Act, you do not need a permit to study in Canada. If your family members, including minor children, want to study in Canada, they must meet the requirements.\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate is in a position to assist you with enrolling in a recognized university, college or school in Canada, Please speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"><div class="more"></div>\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Canada Study Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'canada-study-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:19:51', '2014-11-14 16:19:51', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=107', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(108, 1, '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 Over a 100,000 students go to study in Canada every year and even more come to Canada to learn English or French. \r\n<br><br>\r\nBefore you can apply for a study permit, you must have been accepted at a recognized school, university or college in Canada. You must also show evidence that you can financially support yourself. \r\n<br><br>\r\nYou will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself during your studies. This is calculated using system. The total amount you must be able to show will vary depending on the place and type of study you are undertaking.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo get a clear understanding of how much you will need, and how you will need to prove it, contact Global Migrate''s trained advisors.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOnce you enter Canada you must also prove that you are a Law-abiding citizen in the country of your residence and do not hold any criminal record. The Canadian government may ask you to provide a police certificate. You must be of sound health and if required will be happy to take a medical test. Last but by no means least you must be able to satisfy an immigration officer that you intend to leave Canada at the end of your education.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal Migrate also has a specialist team which works directly with recognised Universities and Colleges in Canada to secure an offer of study for you. \r\n<br><br>\r\nPlease speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit\r\n					 </p>\r\n                     <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n                     <p>\r\n                     In some cases, you do not require a study permit to go to school in Canada.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to study in a short-term course or program\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou do not need a study permit if you plan to take a course or program in Canada that lasts six months or less. You must complete the course or program within the period authorized for your stay in Canada\r\n\r\n</p><h4>Foreign representatives to Canada</h4>\r\nIf you are a family member or staff member of a foreign representative to Canada accredited by Foreign Affairs and International Trade Canada, you may not need a permit to study in Canada.\r\n\r\n<h4>Members of foreign armed forces</h4>\r\nIf you are a member of a foreign armed force under the Visiting Forces Act, you do not need a permit to study in Canada. If your family members, including minor children, want to study in Canada, they must meet the requirements.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate is in a position to assist you with enrolling in a recognized university, college or school in Canada, Please speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit\r\n                     <p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Canada Study Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '2013-12-05 12:27:32', '', 107, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=108', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(109, 1, '2013-12-05 12:28:12', '2013-12-05 12:28:12', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				  A Canadian citizen or permanent resident may sponsor their spouse, common-law partner or conjugal partner to move to Canada to live with them.<br><br>\r\nAn application for Family Class sponsorship can be made if your spouse, common-law or conjugal partner  live inside or outside Canada.<br><br>\r\nAll applicants for permanent residence must go through medical, criminal and background screening.<br><br>\r\nTo be eligible for this type of visa, the foreign national and their spouse must be married or in a civil partnership. If you are not yet married, you can apply for a fiancé visa instead. If you aren’t sure what visa you need, request a call back from one of Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nFor a successful application, you’ll need to provide proof of your marriage and relationship. This includes documents like a marriage certificate along with information about how and when you met your spouse.<br><br>\r\nTo be a sponsor, you must be 18 years of age or older.<br><br>\r\nLodging the application for a marriage visa can be stressful, and requires a lot of documentation. Before you start, call Global-Migrate for a free immigration assessment. We can help save you the hassle and expense of a refusal. With a high success rate and excellent customer service, Global-Migrate can take the stress of applying away.<br><br>\r\nPlease call us now on +44 (0) 207 993 4762 to discuss your application or use our free assessment form below and we will be in touch.\r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="