(111, 1, '2013-12-05 12:29:06', '2013-12-05 12:29:06', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                  Canada is a North American country consisting of ten provinces and three territories. Located in the northern part of the continent, it extends from the Atlantic Ocean in the east to the Pacific Ocean in the west and northward into the Arctic Ocean. It is the world’s second largest country by total area. Canada’s common border with the United States to the south and northwest is the longest in the<br>\r\n<br>\r\n world.\r\n\r\nEvery year Canada attracts more than 5 million people as a tourist, student or temporary worker. People visit Canada to enjoy the many opportunities the country has to offer.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou will need to meet certain entry requirements depending on your nationality and your reasons to visit. Nationals of certain countries do not require a Visa to visit Canada.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIf you are required to apply for a visit visa to Canada, you will need to state reasons of your visit, the duration of the visit, proof of accommodation arrangements and funds to support you and your dependants for the entire stay.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThis type of visa allows you to enter Canada and stay there for up to 6 months. You are not allowed to work on this type of visa.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nHow long it takes to process your application varies depending on the visa office where you applied. Generally it takes between 19 &ndash; 49 days.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou may need to go for an interview with a visa officer. This will depend on the individuals application. You may also be required to take a medical examination to be allowed to enter Canada. If you do, a Canadian immigration officer will tell you and will send you instructions about what to do. A medical examination can add more than three months to the processing time of your application.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIt is always advisable to seek professional help for this type of visa as a slight error in your application or a mistake in your documents may result in your application being rejected and you will loose your application fee. Global-Migrate assists hunderds of applicants weekly with there visit visa appication to Canada.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n To get it right the first time please call us on +44 (0)207 9934762 \r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Visit Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'visit-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:21:07', '2014-11-14 16:21:07', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=111', 0, 'page', '', 0),
