(117, 1, '2013-12-05 12:31:10', '2013-12-05 12:31:10', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 The Canadian government used to allow entrepreneurs to enter the country for the purpose of starting their own business. This program was stopped in 2011, though.<br><br>\r\nIn the past, you were required to meet certain financial and work experience requirements, along with the selection criteria for the Entrepreneur Program.<br><br>\r\nOf course, there are many other visa types available today. Those wishing to migrate to Canada as entrepreneurs may be eligible for a different type of visa. To find out about other visas, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s team of trained advisors today.<br><br>\r\nWe offer a free initial visa assessment that can determine the right type of visa for you, and whether you’re likely to be successful. We only take on cases that we believe will be successful, meaning we won’t waste your time or give you false hope. Our consultants know what a big step immigration is, and our service aims to take the confusion out of the process.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re an entrepreneur looking to immigrate to Canada, we can work with you to find the right way for you to move. Although the Entrepreneur Visa program is not accepting new applications, we can help you with other visa categories.<br><br>\r\nFor those who are in Canada on an existing Entrepreneur Visa, Global-Migrate can help with any other visa questions you might have, including how family members can join you in Canada.<br><br>\r\nWhatever your personal circumstances, Global-Migrate can give you trustworthy and helpful advice about your Canadian immigration. Call or email today to get started!<br><br>\r\n\r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left