(133, 1, '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">The United Kingdom is a popular place, with people wishing to immigrate for all sorts of reasons. At Global-Migrate, we help people make their immigration dreams come true. We have worked on thousands of cases, and our high success rate has established us as the most trusted name in the UK immigration industry.\r\n<h4>Reasons for immigration</h4>\r\nThere are lots of reasons why you might want to immigrate to the UK, and the UK has different visas for each reason. Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors can help you determine which visa category you should apply for, and can assess whether you’ll qualify for a visa.\r\n\r\nEach type of visa has its own rules and regulations, and Global-Migrate can help you make a successful application. To avoid a rejection, you want to be certain you have done everything right and provided all the necessary information.\r\n<a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>Complicated process made easy</h4>\r\nImmigration rules change regularly, though, so it’s important to keep up to date. If this seems overwhelming, don’t worry. That’s what Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors are here for. We’ll help make the immigration process straightforward and successful for you.\r\n\r\nThe visa application process can be complicated. We train our advisors and senior case workers to be able to deal with even the more difficult cases. We’re committed to our clients’ success and are able to help with your application, regardless of how complicated it might be.\r\n<a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>Types of Visa</h4>\r\nUK visas fall into several categories. They each have more than one type of visa within them, and each visa has its own requirements.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Family visas:</strong> These include fiancé visas, marriage visas, and family dependent visas. They generally cover situations where you’re going to the UK to be with your family.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Settlement and Naturalisation:</strong> This are the steps you take to stay in the UK permanently, either as a British citizen or not.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Working visas:</strong> These visas are part of the points-based system and cover situations in which you’re coming to the UK to take up work.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Student visas:</strong> These visas are another part of the points-based system and allow you to come to the UK to study at an approved academic institution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n<div class="more"></div</a>></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'UK Immigration - Global Migrate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'uk-immigration-global-migrate', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=133', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(134, 1, '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				 </p><p>The United Kingdom is a popular place, with people wishing to immigrate for all sorts of reasons. At Global-Migrate, we help people make their immigration dreams come true. We have worked on thousands of cases, and our high success rate has established us as the most trusted name in the UK immigration industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Reasons for immigration</h4>\r\n<p>There are lots of reasons why you might want to immigrate to the UK, and the UK has different visas for each reason. Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors can help you determine which visa category you should apply for, and can assess whether you’ll qualify for a visa.<br><br>\r\nEach type of visa has its own rules and regulations, and Global-Migrate can help you make a successful application. To avoid a rejection, you want to be certain you have done everything right and provided all the necessary information.<br><br>\r\n</p>\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n\r\n<p></p><h4>Complicated process made easy</h4>\r\nImmigration rules change regularly, though, so it’s important to keep up to date. If this seems overwhelming, don’t worry. That’s what Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors are here for. We’ll help make the immigration process straightforward and successful for you.<br><br>\r\nThe visa application process can be complicated. We train our advisors and senior case workers to be able to deal with even the more difficult cases. We’re committed to our clients’ success and are able to help with your application, regardless of how complicated it might be.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a><p></p>\r\n<h4>Types of Visa</h4>\r\nUK visas fall into several categories. They each have more than one type of visa within them, and each visa has its own requirements.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Family visas:</strong> These include fiancé visas, marriage visas, and family dependent visas. They generally cover situations where you’re going to the UK to be with your family.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Settlement and Naturalisation:</strong> This are the steps you take to stay in the UK permanently, either as a British citizen or not.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Working visas:</strong> These visas are part of the points-based system and cover situations in which you’re coming to the UK to take up work. </li>\r\n<li><strong>Student visas:</strong> These visas are another part of the points-based system and allow you to come to the UK to study at an approved academic institution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left"> </td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Immigration - Global Migrate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '2013-12-05 12:40:33', '', 133, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=134', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(135, 1, '2013-12-05 12:44:35', '2013-12-05 12:44:35', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>Welcome to Global Migrate Visas, the world''s leading UK immigration experts.  We offer a unique team of UK immigration lawyers, former immigration officers and experienced immigration specialists to ensure our clients receive the best advice from people who care.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src="images/img-uk.jpg">\r\nThere are a wide range of UK visas on offer, each with different rules and expectations. It can be tricky to understand which bracket you fall in as an individual, which is where our expert help and advice becomes useful. With our professional and qualified UK immigration experts, you can resolve the complicated issue of a UK visa in no time. Feel free to use our FREE assessment tool to determine which Visa is relevant to you, or alternatively follow the links and read in further depth. </p>\r\n<a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\r\nEconomic migration is a key factor in UK immigration policy, and permitting skilled immigration to the UK brings the necessary skills and experience for economic growth. For corporate inquiries, please visit our corporate services page to see how we can assist your company.\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nThe UK visas are divided into five tiers, each with a specific purpose.\r\n</p><h4>Tier One - UK Visas for Highly Skilled Migrants</h4>\r\nIf you have a professional trade which may benefit the UK (such as a GP or a teacher) then you may have enough education points to qualify for permanent residency in the UK.\r\n<h4>Tier Two - UK Visas for Medium and Highly Skilled Workers</h4>\r\nYou can apply for this UK visa application if you have received an offer of employment by a UK company which is based in Britain.\r\n<h4>Tier Five - Short Term Workers</h4>\r\nThis UK visa application will allow short term workers to work in the UK on a temporary basis. Anyone between the ages of 18 to 30 can apply through this UK visa application as part of the ''Youth Mobility Scheme'' which will allow young people to live and work in the country on a working holiday.\r\n<h4>Other UK Immigration Solutions</h4>\r\nThe UK also offers the Post Study Work Programme, which is similar to Tiers 4 and 5. If you are seeking a Family Based Visa please follow the links to the Marriage Visa, Fiancé Visa, Ancestry Visa and De Facto Visa pages.\r\n<p></p>\r\n</td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'uk-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=135', 0, 'page', '', 0),
