(169, 1, '2013-12-05 13:00:50', '2013-12-05 13:00:50', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n				  <p>Tier 1 (Exceptional talent) is for people who are internationally recognised as world leaders or potential world-leading talent in the fields of science and the arts, and who wish to work in the UK.</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">You cannot apply under Tier 1 (Exceptional talent) if you are already in the UK.</span></p>\r\n<p>Tier 1 Exceptional talent is a new entry in the UKBA’s points-based system, which is for migrants from outside the UK or any other part of Europe. If an applicant is a national of a country in the European Economic Area (EEA) or Switzerland or they are a British overseas territories citizen, unless they are from one of the sovereign base areas in Cyprus they do not need to apply for this visa. An applicant is also exempted from applying for the Tier 1 Exceptional talent category if they are a Commonwealth citizen with permission to enter or stay in the UK because at least one of their grandparents were born here. On the other hand if and applicant does not have any conditions or time limit attached to their stay they do not need to apply under this category.</p>\r\n<p></p><h4>Limit on Tier 1 (Exceptional talent) applications</h4>\r\nThe UK government has limited the number of applications that can be made under the Tier 1 Exceptional talent visa category.<p></p>\r\n<p>Every initial application must be endorsed by a ‘designated competent body’. There is a limit of 1,000 endorsements between 6 April 2012 and 5 April 2013.</p>\r\n<p>The endorsements will be assigned to the designated competent bodies in 2 phases: 500 will be available from 6 April 2012 to 30 September, and the second 500 from 1 October 2012 to 5 April 2013.</p>\r\n<p>To find out more or to check your eligibility for this visa please call us on +44 (0)207 9934763 or take our free online visa eligibility below</p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Tier 1 - Exceptional Talent Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tier-1-exceptional-talent-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=169', 0, 'page', '', 0),
