n sentence. If a sponsor has issued a sponsorship certificate in error, all of the non-EU people they have sponsored may be forced to stop work and could be given 28 days to leave the UK.<br><br>\r\nBecoming a licensed sponsor is a big step. The process can be difficult, but the rewards are great. If you’re thinking about becoming a Tier 2 sponsor, get in touch with Global-Migrate today. We’ll provide you with a free initial assessment of your application.<br><br>\r\n\r\n </p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Tier 2 - Sponsorship Licence', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '179-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 13:07:55', '2013-12-05 13:07:55', '', 179, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=180', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(181, 1, '2013-12-05 13:08:55', '2013-12-05 13:08:55', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n				 The United Kingdom is home to some of the world’s most prestigious universities and schools. Each year, people come from all over the world to study at these academic institutions. For those coming from outside the European Economic Area (EEA), a Tier 4 Student Visa is required.<br><br>\r\nTo get a Tier 4 visa, you need to have an offer to study at an approved institution. Each institution will have its own admission requirements that you must meet in order to receive the Confirmation of Acceptance for Studies (CAS).<br><br>\r\nThe UK Border Agency regularly updates the list of institutions that are allowed to sponsor overseas students. Global Migrate can advise you on whether your institution is on the list or not.<br><br>\r\nYou will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself during your studies. This is calculated using a points-based system. The total amount you must be able to show will vary depending on the place and type of study you are undertaking.<br><br>\r\nOverseas students do pay higher fees than UK students. The cost of courses can range from £7,000 per year to £18,000 per year. The cost of living during studies can also vary, with London being much higher than other parts of the country. <br><br>\r\nTo get a clear understanding of how much you will need, and how you will need to prove it, contact Global Migrate’s trained advisors.<br><br>\r\nA Tier 4 visa does have limitations on it. Because the purpose of your stay is to study, you will have limits on how much you can work each week. You might also have limits on the type of jobs you may take.<br><br>\r\nIf you are applying for a Tier 4 visa, you might be able to bring your family with you. Get in touch with a Global migrate advisor to find out more about the requirements for families under Tier 4 visas.<br><br>\r\nStudying in the UK can be a very exciting and fulfilling thing, so don’t let the visa process stop you. Global Migrate has a team of experienced immigration advisors who are ready to help you with your application. Call today for an assessment.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Tier 4 - Student Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tier-4-student-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=181', 0, 'page', '', 0),
