(190, 1, '2013-12-05 13:11:53', '2013-12-05 13:11:53', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> Citizens of Commonwealth nations may be eligible for an ancestry visa in the United Kingdom. This type of visa allows you to live and work in the UK for a period of 5 years, after which you can apply for a settlement visa to stay permanently.<br><br>\r\nAncestry visas must be applied for fro outside the UK. If you are already in the UK, you will not be able to switch to an ancestry visa from another category. If you are currently in the UK, contact Global-Migrate to find out about your visa options.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Ancestry Requirements</strong><br><br>\r\nThe basic requirements for the ancestry visa are straightforward.\r\n</p><ul>\r\n<li>You must be a Commonwealth citizen</li>\r\n<li>You must be 17 or older</li>\r\n<li>You must be able to work when you come to the UK and be able to support yourself without public funds</li>\r\n<li>You must have at least one British grandparent.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou’ll need to show your ancestry through birth certificates, marriage certificates, and adoption certificates, if applicable. You can’t claim ancestry on the basis of step-parents, but you can claim through adoption. If you’re not sure whether you are able to apply based on your ancestry, call Global-Migrate for a free assessment.<br><br>\r\nIf you are granted an ancestry visa, your family will be able to come with you, or join you in the UK. This includes your husband, wife, or civil partner, as well as any children under the age of 18. To apply for an ancestry visa and entry clearance for family members, get in touch with Global-Migrate.<br><br>\r\nThe ancestry visa can be an ideal choice for those who qualify. The application does require proof of your grandparent’s citizenship, and you will need to provide plenty of documentation. If you have any questions about the application process, or if you want help with your application, get in touch today. We’re happy to provide a free visa assessment to determine if your application will be successful.<br><br>\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Ancestry Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '189-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-05 13:11:53', '2013-12-05 13:11:53', '', 189, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?p=190', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(191, 1, '2013-12-05 13:12:51', '2013-12-05 13:12:51', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you are in the United Kingdom on a visa, you might be able to extend your stay. The application for an extension is often slightly different than for the original visa. However, you will still need to provide proof that you are eligible to be in the UK.<br><br>\r\nAt Global-Migrate, we have helped thousands of people extend their visa. To find out how we can help with your visa extension, call us today.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 1 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend your stay on a Tier 1 visa, you will need to provide the same evidence that you did when you applied for your initial visa. Depending on which category of Tier 1 visa you hold, the rules for extensions have changed recently. Our visa assessment can help determine what extension options are available to you.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 2 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend a Tier 2 visa, your employer will need to submit the application. In most cases, your initial visa will have been for 5 years, after which time you can apply for a settlement, or indefinite leave to remain, visa. If your visa was for less than 5 years, or you do not want to apply for settlement, you may be able to extend your Tier 2 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine how best to extend your Tier 2 stay.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 4 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend your Tier 4 visa, you will need to show that you are still enrolled at your academic institution. While your initial visa is granted for the entire time of your course, you might need to extend your stay if it is taking you longer to complete your course. If you have been accepted into another course, such as for a postgraduate degree, you might be able to apply for an extension from within the UK. Global-Migrate’s advisors can help determine your Tier 4 extension options.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Other categories</strong><br><br>\r\nIf you are in the UK on any other type of visa, you may still be able to extend your stay. Call Global-Migrate today to discuss visa extensions and transfers. We’re committed to the highest levels of customer service and pride ourselves in being able to help all of our clients with their immigration dreams.<br><br>\r\n</p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Visa Extensions &ndash; Extend UK Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'uk-visa-extensions-extend-uk-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=191', 0, 'page', '', 0),
