(214, 1, '2013-12-05 13:28:44', '2013-12-05 13:28:44', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n     If you want to temporarily work and live in the United States, you may be able eligible for an H-1B visa. This visa will allow you to stay in the US for three years, and can be extended for another three years. At the end of this period, you may be eligible to apply for permanent residency.<br><br>\r\nThe number of H-1B visas issued each year is strictly capped, meaning there is frequently high competition for this type of visa. If you want to find out more about this and other visa options for you, speak to one of Global-Migrate’s immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nH1-B visas are intended to allow American companies to hire foreign workers for specialty occupations that require theoretical or practical application of highly specialized knowledge. This means that not every worker, and not every job, is eligible for the H-1B visa. Global-Migrate’s qualified immigration consultants can help you find out if your occupation and experience is suitable.<br><br>\r\nThe visa petition is made by your US employer, not by you. However, you will most likely have to provide evidence that you can qualify for a job offer. This includes having proof of the required education level and certifications.<br><br>\r\nOnce approved, the H-1B visa will allow you to work in the specified position. If the job ends before the visa expires, you might be able to change jobs. For more advice about changing jobs, call Global-Migrate to speak to an advisor.<br><br>\r\nIt is necessary that you be on the payroll of an American company for the duration of your visa. You may also need to pay US income taxes. If you intend to work in the United States for a foreign company, you may need a different type of visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine the right visa for you.<br><br>\r\nThe H-1B visa process can be complicated, so it is helpful to speak to an immigration advisor before starting. To receive a free visa assessment, email or call Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA H1B Visa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'usa-h1b-visa', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '2014-11-14 16:20:53', '', 0, 'http://creativewebdesignlondon.com/global-migrat/?page_id=214', 0, 'page', '', 0),
