(278, 1, '2014-03-07 07:23:42', '2014-03-07 07:23:42', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Global Migrate now represents several top ranking educational institutions of U.K. We can help students from all over the world to get admission in these colleges and complete their education pro-actively in keeping with global market trends.\n\nGlobal Migrate has developed a portfolio of specialised courses which lead to undergraduate degrees, Masters degrees and professional qualifications that can be individually tailored to the specific career aspirations of all students.\n<ul>\n	<li>Foundation</li>\n	<li>Pre-Masters</li>\n	<li>MBA</li>\n	<li>Business</li>\n	<li>Economics</li>\n	<li>Computing / IT</li>\n	<li>Development Studies</li>\n	<li>Art and Design</li>\n	<li>TESOL / Linguistics</li>\n	<li>International Relations</li>\n	<li>Sociology</li>\n	<li>Medicine</li>\n	<li>Music</li>\n	<li>Architecture</li>\n	<li>Law</li>\n	<li>Sports Science</li>\n	<li>Film Studies</li>\n	<li>Drama/Acting</li>\n	<li>Colleges</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>UK University Applications</h4>\n<strong>Global Migrate (Official UK University Application Centre)</strong>\n\nApplying to UK universities though Global Migrate is simple and free.\n\n\nGlobal Migrate will help you apply and get into your chosen university. Follow the steps below to get an offer from a UK University.\n<ul>\n	<li>Come meet our UK university counsellors and receive advice in your language</li>\n	<li>For students unable to come to the office we provide online counselling services</li>\n	<li>Our UK university counsellors will help you prepare your documents for your applications</li>\n	<li>We offer IELTS preparation courses to help you reach the English level needed for UK universities</li>\n	<li>Come to our office and our counsellors will check and submit your applications to UK universities</li>\n	<li>You will receive your offer letter in approximately 2-8 weeks</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\n</a>\n<div class="more"></div></td>\n<td align="right">\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="10"></td>\n<td width="20"></td>\n<td width="36"></td>\n<td width="34"></td>\n<td width="41"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Apply to UK University', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '252-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:23:42', '2014-03-07 07:23:42', '', 252, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/252-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
