(290, 1, '2014-03-07 07:32:53', '2014-03-07 07:32:53', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                Moving to Australia can be a great decision. It is a beautiful country, and one that has many draws for people all over the world. If you’re planning a move to Australia, you’ll want to speak to one of Global-Migrate’s qualified immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nYour reasons for moving to Australia will determine which type of visa you need. Some visas are intended for family members of Australian nationals, while others are for those who are going to Australia for work purposes. To find out which visa is right for you, start your free visa assessment now.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re looking to move to Australia for work, you might be able to get a visa on the basis of your work experience and training. You can also get an employer to sponsor your visa application. For people aged between 18 and 30, it is also possible to apply for the very popular working holiday visa.<br><br>\r\nIf you have family members who are Australian nationals, you might be eligible to join them. In this case, you would need to apply for a special family visa, or a partner visa.<br><br>\r\nWith so many types of visa available, it can be difficult for you to know which is right for you.Our agents can help you through the complex and stressful visa process. They are trained immigration advisors, and are experts at helping people through this life-changing event. <br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate hires agents who are registered with the Migration Agents Registration Authority (MARA). This provides our clients with the best possible service for all their Australian immigration needs. <br><br>\r\nWith fifteen years of experience helping people make their immigration dreams come true, we are one of the world’s largest and most successful immigration consultancies. If you’re considering a move to Australia, call us today for a free visa assessment.<br><br>\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        ', 'Australia Visa and Immigration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:32:53', '2014-03-07 07:32:53', '', 43, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(291, 1, '2014-03-07 07:33:24', '2014-03-07 07:33:24', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                 \r\n                 Skilled migrant visa is an option for highly skilled people to immigrate to Australia on a permanent basis. Skilled migrants have always been welcome in most countries but Australia offers more rewarding opportunities in the form of high salaries, career growth and stability than any other country. Get in touch with Global Migrate now to find out if you qualify as a skilled migrant for Australi\r\n<br><br>\r\nSkilled migrants have three different options for Australia ;\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Skilled Independent Visa - (Subclass 189)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Independent visa is a points-based application. To qualify for the independent visa, you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements, you will be eligible for this visa. This visa is without a doubt the most desired route of immigration to Australia; however, you need to score very high points to be able to apply for this visa. This is an independent application which means no state, or territory will sponsor you and you need to score the required points without having to claim any bonus points for sponsorship.\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-189.html">Read More...</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated Visa &ndash; (Subclass 190)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Sponsored visa is a points-based application. To qualify for this type of visa you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements you may be eligible for this visa. Once approved you become a permanent resident of Australia from day one however you have a restriction to your stay in Australia, where you need to live in the region that sponsors your occupation for at least 24 months.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-190.html">Read More...</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Visa &ndash; (Subclass 489) </h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Regional Sponsored visa is initially based on meeting a point score. To qualify for this visa, you must first pass basic requirements. You get points for your age, English competence, training, work experience and having an eligible relative (or a state) able to sponsor you. Once you meet these requirements, you may be eligible for this type of visa. This is initially a 3 year visa sponsored by a state.\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-489.html">Read More... </a></strong></p>\r\n                  <p></p> \r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n', 'Australian Skilled Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '69-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:33:24', '2014-03-07 07:33:24', '', 69, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/69-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(292, 1, '2014-03-07 07:34:37', '2014-03-07 07:34:37', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                 If you want to work in Australia, you might be eligible for a work visa, also known as a work permit or subclass 457 visa. To be eligible for this type of visa, you need to be sponsored by an employer to fill a nominated skilled position, have the relevant skills for the job, and have health insurance.<br><br>\r\nIf you think this might be right for you, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s team of trained immigration advisors today for a visa assessment.\r\nThere are several different types of working visas available for Australia, so it’s important to make sure you apply for the right one. Our MARA registered consultants can help you navigate the complex visa process.<br><br>\r\nA subclass 457 visa will allow you to work in Australia for up to four years. You’ll also be able to bring your family with you, and travel in and out of Australia as often as you want. <br><br>\r\nOnly some occupations are included in this type of Australian work visa. You must also meet a specific skill and experience level for that occupation. Working with a qualified immigration advisor from Global-Migrate can help you determine if you meet these requirements.\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou must also be able to demonstrate that you have suitable knowledge of the English language. However, there are some occupations that are exempted from this requirement. To find out more about which occupations are exempt, call Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\n\r\nGetting an Australian work permit can be a great step for you, and can give you valuable career advancement. The application process for any visa can be complex and confusing, so it is worth getting help with your application.<br><br>\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s visa advisors can help you with your application, and can help you submit a decision-ready application. This will help speed up your application, meaning you can begin your work in Australia sooner.<br><br>\r\n\r\nCall, email, or request a call back from Global-Migrate’s team of advisors today!<br><br>\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n  ', 'Australian Work Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:34:37', '2014-03-07 07:34:37', '', 71, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/71-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(293, 1, '2014-03-07 07:34:49', '2014-03-07 07:34:49', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                <p>\r\n				 Becoming a British citizen is the last step in the immigration process. Through naturalisation, immigrants are given the same rights as those born in the UK. If you have been granted a settlement visa, or indefinite leave to remain, applying for citizenship is the final immigration service available.<br><br>\r\nThere are several ways to apply for British citizenship. Speak to one of Global-Migrate’s immigration experts to find out the best path based on your current citizenship and visa status.\r\nTo apply for citizenship, you will need to have been living and working in the UK for three to five years. The exact amount of time will depend on your current visa category. For people living in the UK as the married spouse or civil partner of a British citizen, you will need to be resident for three years. To check the residence requirement for your case, call Global-Migrate for more information and a free assessment.<br><br>\r\nThe citizenship application includes requirements that are not found in visa applications. You will need to be of sound mind, meaning you are able to make your own decisions.<br><br>\r\nFor anyone over 10 years of age who is not stateless, you will need to demonstrate good character. This includes acting lawfully and paying taxes. Your criminal background will also be checked, and you will be asked about participation in any war crimes or genocide.<br><br>\r\nIf you are considering making an application for British citizenship, it is highly recommended that you speak to an immigration advisor first. With fifteen years of experience, Global-Migrate is a leading expert in immigration, and we can help you with your citizenship application.<br><br>\r\nWe work with hundreds of applicants every year, and our highly trained case workers keep up to date with all the changing immigration regulations. If you want to become a British citizen, get in touch with Global-Migrate today to discuss your path to naturalization.\r\n</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'British Citizenship', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '139-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:34:49', '2014-03-07 07:34:49', '', 139, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/139-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2014-03-07 07:35:01', '2014-03-07 07:35:01', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                Canada has a lot to offer, with a diverse population, wide variety of jobs, and unparalleled natural beauty. If you’re thinking about moving to Canada, you might be overwhelmed by all the types of visa available, though.\r\nGlobal-Migrate is an experienced immigration advisor, and we have helped many people figure out how to make their Canada immigration dream a reality. If you want to get started now, get in touch for your free visa assessment today.\r\n</p><h4>Working in Canada</h4>\r\nIf you want to migrate to Canada for work, there are several different visas available. One of the most popular Canadian visas is the Federal Skilled Worker visa. This points-based visa gives you permanent residency and the freedom to work in Canada. You can also apply for a work permit, which will allow you to work for a specific employer in Canada. \r\nGlobal-Migrate can help you apply for any Canadian working visa, and can help you determine which visa is right for you. Get in touch with us today to begin your application. We work closely with employers in Canada and can also help you find a position for a work permit.\r\n<h4>Studying in Canada</h4>\r\nCanada is home to many great universities, and is a popular destination for education. If you are planning to attend a Canadian educational institution, we can help you prepare your visa application. If you’re looking to change from a student visa to a different category, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s trained immigration consultants for advice and help with your application.\r\n<h4>Family in Canada</h4>\r\nAnother popular visa category is the Canadian family visas. These allow the spouse, parents, and children of Canadian nationals to join them in Canada. Depending on what relationship you have with the Canadian national, you’ll need to provide different information and proof. Global-Migrate has helped many people join their family in Canada, and we can help you, too.\r\nCanada offers these and many other ways to live in the country. We offer a free initial assessment to determine the best visa option for your individual case. Call Global-Migrate today to take the first step in making your Canada immigration dream a reality!\r\n\r\n                      <p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Canada Immigration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '101-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:35:01', '2014-03-07 07:35:01', '', 101, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/101-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(295, 1, '2014-03-07 07:35:09', '2014-03-07 07:35:09', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Canada Spouse Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '121-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:35:09', '2014-03-07 07:35:09', '', 121, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/121-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(296, 1, '2014-03-07 07:35:20', '2014-03-07 07:35:20', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 Over a 100,000 students go to study in Canada every year and even more come to Canada to learn English or French. \r\n<br><br>\r\nBefore you can apply for a study permit, you must have been accepted at a recognized school, university or college in Canada. You must also show evidence that you can financially support yourself. \r\n<br><br>\r\nYou will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself during your studies. This is calculated using system. The total amount you must be able to show will vary depending on the place and type of study you are undertaking.\r\n<br><br>\r\nTo get a clear understanding of how much you will need, and how you will need to prove it, contact Global Migrate''s trained advisors.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOnce you enter Canada you must also prove that you are a Law-abiding citizen in the country of your residence and do not hold any criminal record. The Canadian government may ask you to provide a police certificate. You must be of sound health and if required will be happy to take a medical test. Last but by no means least you must be able to satisfy an immigration officer that you intend to leave Canada at the end of your education.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal Migrate also has a specialist team which works directly with recognised Universities and Colleges in Canada to secure an offer of study for you. \r\n<br><br>\r\nPlease speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit\r\n					 </p>\r\n                     <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n                     <p>\r\n                     In some cases, you do not require a study permit to go to school in Canada.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to study in a short-term course or program\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou do not need a study permit if you plan to take a course or program in Canada that lasts six months or less. You must complete the course or program within the period authorized for your stay in Canada\r\n\r\n</p><h4>Foreign representatives to Canada</h4>\r\nIf you are a family member or staff member of a foreign representative to Canada accredited by Foreign Affairs and International Trade Canada, you may not need a permit to study in Canada.\r\n\r\n<h4>Members of foreign armed forces</h4>\r\nIf you are a member of a foreign armed force under the Visiting Forces Act, you do not need a permit to study in Canada. If your family members, including minor children, want to study in Canada, they must meet the requirements.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate is in a position to assist you with enrolling in a recognized university, college or school in Canada, Please speak to our Canadian Student advisor on +44 207 993 4762 today to see if you are eligible for a Canadian study permit\r\n                     <p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Canada Study Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:35:20', '2014-03-07 07:35:20', '', 107, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/107-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(297, 1, '2014-03-07 07:35:29', '2014-03-07 07:35:29', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 If you want to work in Canada, you’ll need the right type of visa. For temporary jobs, you’ll need a work permit.<br><br>\r\nA Canadian Work Permit allows you to work for a specific employer. This employer sponsors your application, and they must be able to demonstrate that they cannot fill the job with local workers.<br><br>\r\nAlthough a work permit does not allow you to live in Canada permanently, it can be extended in certain circumstances. If you want to have permanent residency in Canada, or don’t have a job offer in place, you will need to apply for a different type of visa, such as the Skilled Worker visa.\r\nIf you aren’t sure which visa is right for you, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s team of qualified immigration advisors today. We offer a free initial visa assessment that can help determine if you’re eligible for a Work Permit.<br><br>\r\nThe processing times for work permits vary, and certain occupations are given priority. For more information about which occupations require, or don’t require, work permits, call Global-Migrate today. Our consultants have up-to-date information to help you with your immigration dream.\r\nOnce you have your work permit, you’ll also be able to bring your family with you to Canada. They will need to apply to join you, and Global-Migrate’s ICCRC Canadian visa specialist advisor can help you with this application.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate also works closely with Canadian employers to help them sponsor employees. If you would like to sponsor foreign workers, or are looking for an employer to sponsor you, get in touch with Global-Migrate to see how we can help you.<br><br>\r\nWith years of experience, Global-Migrate is a trusted and successful immigration advisor. We can help you make your dream of working in Canada a reality, so call us today!<br><br>\r\n\r\n    	 </p>\r\n         \r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Canada Work Permit', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '105-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:35:29', '2014-03-07 07:35:29', '', 105, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/105-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
