(304, 1, '2014-03-07 07:38:24', '2014-03-07 07:38:24', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                  Currently Denmark has a shortage of skilled workers in certain fields. This list is known as the Positive list.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThe list is subject to change at any moment of time therefore please call us to find out if your occupation is on the list.  The most recent change was on the 1st of January, which has affected some people. To avoid disappointment you must contact our Danish Immigration specialist by either calling us or taking our free eligibility assessment.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMost common occupations on the list are;\r\n</p><ul>\r\n<li>Engineers</li>\r\n	<li>Dentist and Doctors</li>\r\n	<li>Attorneys</li>\r\n	<li>Deputy Judge</li>\r\n	<li>Auditor</li>\r\n	<li>Geologist</li>\r\n	<li>Marine Biologist</li>\r\n	<li>Psychologist</li>\r\n	<li>IT consultants/Programmers</li>\r\n	<li>Nurse</li>\r\n	<li>Midwife</li>\r\n	<li>Teachers</li>\r\n<li>Childcarer</li>\r\n<li>Social Educators</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRecently Denmark Immigration has been on the rise and many people from all over the world have been applying for a visa to Denmark, specialy via the Green Card Route.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you have education or work experience in any of the above occupations than please call Global Migrate today on 02079934762 or fill out our free assessment form using the tool below \r\n                   <p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Denmark Positive List', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '131-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:38:24', '2014-03-07 07:38:24', '', 131, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/131-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(305, 1, '2014-03-07 07:38:32', '2014-03-07 07:38:32', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you are a national of the European Economic Area or Switzerland, you’ll be able to come to the United Kingdom. You have the right to live and work in the UK, provided you are able to support yourself without any government assistance. For advice about entering the UK as a EEA national, and your rights in the UK, get in touch with our team of trained advisors.<br><br>\r\nIf you are the family member of an EEA national, but from outside the EEA yourself, you will need a family permit to enter the UK. This is similar to a visa, and allows you to live and work in the United Kingdom. Family members include husbands, wives, civil partners, dependent children under 21, and dependent parents or grandparents.<br><br>\r\nYou will need to apply for, and be granted, this permit before you enter the United Kingdom. You will also need to be travelling to the UK with the EEA national or to join an EEA national who is already in the UK.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> </a></p><div class="more"></div><br>\r\nThere are limits to the family permit, though. They are only intended for those looking to join a non-UK EEA national in the UK. If you are joining a UK national, you will need to apply for the appropriate visa. There are exceptions to this, including if the UK national is a resident of an EEA country. If you are unsure about whether the EEA family permit is right for you, contact Global-Migrate for an assessment.<br><br>\r\nThe rules for EEA family permits are different than for a standard visa. We have helped over 20,000 people with EEA applications, and can provide you with a free assessment about your application.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate can help you determine if an EEA family permit is right for you, or if you will need to apply for a visa. Our trained advisors keep on top of changing regulations and can give you all the information you need for a successful application.<br><br>\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'EEA Family Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '197-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:38:32', '2014-03-07 07:38:32', '', 197, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/197-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(306, 1, '2014-03-07 07:38:40', '2014-03-07 07:38:40', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                 <p>\r\n                 As migration agents we completely understand that migration to Australia is not just a lengthy process but also complicated. However, with many years or practice and experience we fully understand the standard of work required in your application process for a successful application. It’s not just about complying with all the regulations, it’s as much about presenting the facts of your case in the right way to ensure that your application gets through the system the first time you apply. As a company that hires MARA registered agents we are bound by a strict code of conduct for your protection (MARA Code of Conduct)\r\n<br><br>\r\nAustralian Immigration can be quite a complex and a time consuming process, therefore, we strongly advise you to seek assistance from people in the know how. Speaking to Global Migrate’s knowledgeable immigration advisors will reduce the chance of a rejection in your visa application and most definitely is a wise decision if you are deciding to make a life changing decision for a better future for you and your family.\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou may apply for immigration to Australia via many different routes. You can be a skilled worker whose occupation might be in demand or you might be a school or college leaver who wants to migrate to Australia and get work experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate specialises in all Australian Skilled Migration, Work Permits, Study Visas and Working Holiday Visas for Australia. Our team of MARA consultants are authorised by the Australian Government to give advice and assist you.\r\n<br><br>\r\nPlease call Global Migrate if you require help or advice regarding your <span style="font-weight:bold">Partner’s visa, any other Family Visa, the very popular Skilled Migration program or even a Working Holiday Visa</span>\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can even check your eligibility by using our free assessment button below.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n       ', 'Emigrate Australia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:38:40', '2014-03-07 07:38:40', '', 75, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(307, 1, '2014-03-07 07:38:51', '2014-03-07 07:38:51', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 The Canadian government used to allow entrepreneurs to enter the country for the purpose of starting their own business. This program was stopped in 2011, though.<br><br>\r\nIn the past, you were required to meet certain financial and work experience requirements, along with the selection criteria for the Entrepreneur Program.<br><br>\r\nOf course, there are many other visa types available today. Those wishing to migrate to Canada as entrepreneurs may be eligible for a different type of visa. To find out about other visas, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s team of trained advisors today.<br><br>\r\nWe offer a free initial visa assessment that can determine the right type of visa for you, and whether you’re likely to be successful. We only take on cases that we believe will be successful, meaning we won’t waste your time or give you false hope. Our consultants know what a big step immigration is, and our service aims to take the confusion out of the process.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re an entrepreneur looking to immigrate to Canada, we can work with you to find the right way for you to move. Although the Entrepreneur Visa program is not accepting new applications, we can help you with other visa categories.<br><br>\r\nFor those who are in Canada on an existing Entrepreneur Visa, Global-Migrate can help with any other visa questions you might have, including how family members can join you in Canada.<br><br>\r\nWhatever your personal circumstances, Global-Migrate can give you trustworthy and helpful advice about your Canadian immigration. Call or email today to get started!<br><br>\r\n\r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Entrepreneur Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '117-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:38:51', '2014-03-07 07:38:51', '', 117, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/117-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(308, 1, '2014-03-07 07:39:04', '2014-03-07 07:39:04', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                For some types of Australian visa, you will first need to submit an expression of interest. This preliminary application is not the same as the visa application itself. If your Expression of Interest is successful, you will be given an invitation to apply for the relevant visa.\r\nMuch like a visa application, though, the Expression of Interest can be a confusing and complex process. To get advice and a free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nAn Expression of Interest is required for many skilled worker visas. In your EOI, you will be providing information about your qualifications and experience. This will help Australian immigration determine if you meet the requirements for the program you are interested in.<br><br>\r\nTo file an Expression of Interest, you won’t need to submitting supporting documents. However, if you are invited to apply for a visa, you will need these. Any information you include in your EOI will have to be backed up when it comes time to apply for your visa. Global-Migrate’s consultants can help you prepare for your EOI and visa submission/\r\nSubmitting an incorrect EOI can leave you without an invitation to apply for a visa. This is why it is crucial your EOI is correct, and that you submit it for the right type of visa.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s team of MARA registered consultants can help make sure your Expression of Interest will be successful. We know what is required for each visa program, so can save you the time and hassle of an unsuccessful submission.<br><br>\r\nAt Global-Migrate, we only take on cases that we believe will be successful. Our free initial assessment will help you determine if a skilled migrant visa is right for you. Many people share your dream of working in Australia, and the EOI is the first step to making that dream a reality. <br><br>\r\n\r\n                  </p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n  ', 'Expression of Interest - EOI', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:39:04', '2014-03-07 07:39:04', '', 45, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/45-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(495, 1, '2014-04-24 11:02:04', '2014-04-24 11:02:04', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">The Federal Skilled Worker Visa is a popular way of getting permanent residency in Canada. The points-based program allows those who meet certain criteria to become permanent residents. Global-Migrate has helped thousands of people immigrate to Canada over the years. If you are interested in applying for a Canadian visa, call us today for your free immigration assessment.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Federal Skilled Worker Visa will be accepting new applications from May 2014. Although there will be limited availability for this application. Depending on your occupation you may qualify for this visa. To find out more please get in touch with our Canadian department. When it reopens to new applications, it will use a new points table. Global-Migrate’s immigration advisors can help you plan for an application using the new criteria.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe changing rules for the Federal Skilled Worker Program will still include a many of the same requirements. These include education, language proficiency, work experience, age, whether you have arranged employment, and your adaptability. You will also need to show that you have enough money to support yourself when you get to Canada.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo make sure your application is successful, you’ll need to use the most up to date visa information. Global-Migrate’s expert advisors are on top of all changes to Canadian visa rules, and can help figure out the right category for you. Before you apply on your own, get in touch for a free visa assessment and find out how we can help you.\r\n\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate has a very high success rate for Canadian visa applications, and can help ensure that your visa application is not rejected. Whatever stage you’re at in your visa application, our ICCRC visa experts can provide assistance.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe benefits of a Federal Skilled 