plication, our ICCRC visa experts can provide assistance. <br><br>\r\nThe benefits of a Federal Skilled Worker Visa are huge. It will allow you to liv and work in Canada, and after three years you will become eligible for Canadian citizenship. If you want your dream of immigrating to Canada come true, get in touch with Global-Migrate today to see how we can help.\r\n<br>\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Federal Skilled Worker Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '103-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:39:11', '2014-03-07 07:39:11', '', 103, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/103-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(310, 1, '2014-03-07 07:40:10', '2014-03-07 07:40:10', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you are planning to marry a British national or somebody settled in the United Kingdom, you might be eligible for a UK Fiance Visa. This visa allows you to come to the UK for up to six months before your wedding or civil partnership provided you intend to settle in the UK after it.<br><br>\r\nIf you aren’t sure this is the right category for you, call Global Migrate for help. Our advisors can help you determine which visa category fits your situation.<br><br>\r\nFor a fiancé visa, you and your fiancé must both be over 18 and legally allowed to marry each other. You must have met each other in person, and your relationship must be genuine. You must also demonstrate that you meet certain financial and language requirements.<br><br>\r\nYou will not be allowed to work while in the UK on a fiancé visa, and you must show that you and your partner will be able to support yourselves and any children during this time.<br><br>\r\nThe UK Border Agency provides guidance on how to prove all of this, but for advice about your specific situation, it’s best to speak to a trained immigration adviser at Global Migrate.<br><br>\r\nAs with all UK visas, you’ll also need to meet suitability criteria. These guidelines focus on things like criminal records, past immigration, and similar issues. You will also need to prove that you and your fiancé have suitable accommodation, and that you live together.<br><br>\r\nIf you have been denied a fiancé visa, you have the ability to appeal. Most refusals are because the proper evidence has not been submitted. As Global Migrate, we have our senior advisors check every fiancé visa to ensure you have a strong application with no errors.<br><br>\r\nTo get more information about fiancé visas, call Global Migrate today. With 15 years of experience and a very high success rate, we are experts in fiancé visa applications.<br><br>\r\n</p>\r\n <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left"> </td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Fiance Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '161-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:40:10', '2014-03-07 07:40:10', '', 161, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/161-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(311, 1, '2014-03-07 07:40:47', '2014-03-07 07:40:47', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                 <p>Indefinite Leave to Remain (ILR) allows you to migrate to Britain permanently. It is often referred to as permanent UK residency. As part of this you gain settled status and can apply for British citizenship via <a href="british-citizenship.html"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color:#274789;">naturalisation</span></a>.</p>\r\n<p>An application for permanent residency in the UK can be made by people who have previously been successful in applying for a UK visa in Britain in a category leading to settlement. These categories will say if they are or are not eligible and counted towards the right to remain.</p>\r\n<p>Global-Migrate can help you to obtain anything from a short-term visit visa through to long-term residency and citizenship. We handle everything and anything to do with UK immigration. You can find out whether you qualify by completing our online Indefinite Leave to Remain assessment form today.</p>\r\n<p><strong>ILR Benefits</strong><br><br>\r\nA permanent resident visa for Great Britain has no time limit imposed upon it, and whereas a work permit would depend upon a specific offer of employment, there are no immigration related restrictions upon the type of work or business a person with a permanent UK resident status may undertake on arrival.</p>\r\n<p><strong>ILR Duration</strong><br><br>\r\nThere is no time limit; however, it is important to note that holders should not spend periods of more than two years outside of the United Kingdom. A long-term UK resident should consider the United Kingdom as home and spending only short periods of time in Britain may lead to the loss of ILR.<br>\r\nA person with ILR may be eligible to apply for British Naturalisation as a UK citizen, provided they meet the requirements for <a href="british-citizenship.html"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color:#274789;">British citizenship</span></a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Eligibility</strong><br><br>\r\nThe applicant must have a settled status in Britain. This usually means that the candidate must have been resident in Great Britain on the same visa class for at least four years. The only exception to this is for people on marriage visas or De Facto visas, who only require two years and for periods of exceptionally long-term residency (10 years legal, or 14 years as a combination of illegal and legal residency).</p>\r\n<p>Ancestry and being an EU National can be a way in, as can marriage. All applicants have to demonstrate sufficient understanding of the English language and the English way of life in order to qualify.</p>\r\n<p>Global-Migrate can make an application for you Indefinite Leave to Remain (Also known as the ILR) using one of our premium services, which means that you will have your passport back within 24 hours. Certain categories cannot be applied for using the premium services, for e.g. ILR through <a href="long-term-residency-visa.html"><span style="text-decoration: underline; color:#274789;">long residency</span></a> (10 years legal stay in the UK), partner of an EEA national or an EEA national who has spent 5 years in the UK</p>\r\n<p>The UKBA might not make a decision within 24 hours in some cases even if you opt for the premium service. This will depend on the individuals application.</p>\r\n<p>An application for ILR can only be made 28 days prior to you becoming eligible for the application.</p>\r\n<p>Do you think you qualify for your ILR? To find out more please call us directly on +44 (0)207 9934762 or use our FREE assessment form.</p> <p></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'ILR Visa for UK', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '145-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:40:47', '2014-03-07 07:40:47', '', 145, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/145-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(312, 1, '2014-03-07 07:41:05', '2014-03-07 07:41:05', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n                \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you’re planning on settling permanently in the United Kingdom, you’ll need to apply for a special type of visa that will grant you indefinite leave to remain. Which form you use for the application will depend on why you are in the UK.<br><br>\nThe specific immigration rules can change. Global Migrate can help you determine which rules apply to your case, and can assist you with your application.\n</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits of ILR</strong><br><br>\nIndefinite Leave to Remain will allow you to freely live in the UK with no time limit. You will not need to apply for any extensions, which means you also won’t have any further fees to pay. You can also work without restrictions. This means you will not need any permission or approval to work for different companies, or for yourself.<br><br>\nBecause of these benefits, the settlement visa is a big application. It is advised that you speak to a Global Migrate case worker to ensure that you have filled out the application correctly, and that you have all the evidence required.\n</p>\n<p><strong>Types of settlement visas</strong><br><br>\nThough they all grant indefinite leave to remain, there are multiple types of settlement visa. They differ in terms of what information they need, and what you will need to prove.<br><br>\nThe SET(M) visa is for people who wish to settle permanently in the UK as a married partner or civil partner of a British citizen or somebody already settled in the UK.<br><br>\nSET(O) covers most situations where a person has been in the UK for five years under other types of visa. This includes Tier 1 and Tier 2 visa holders.<br><br>\nOther SET visas are available for special cases such as children of settled people, victims of domestic violence, and retirees of independent means.<br><br>\nTo find out which category applies to you, contact Global Migrate for an assessment and advice on submitting a successful application.<br><br>\n</p> <p></p></td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10"> </td> \n            <td width="20"> </td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'Indefinite Leave to Remain', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '187-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:41:05', '2014-03-07 07:41:05', '', 187, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/187-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(313, 1, '2014-03-07 07:41:07', '2014-03-07 07:41:07', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you’re planning on settling permanently in the United Kingdom, you’ll need to apply for a special type of visa that will grant you indefinite leave to remain. Which form you use for the application will depend on why you are in the UK.<br><br>\r\nThe specific immigration rules can change. Global Migrate can help you determine which rules apply to your case, and can assist you with your application.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of ILR</strong><br><br>\r\nIndefinite Leave to Remain will allow you to freely live in the UK with no time limit. You will not need to apply for any extensions, which means you also won’t have any further fees to pay. You can also work without restrictions. This means you will not need any permission or approval to work for different companies, or for yourself.<br><br>\r\nBecause of these benefits, the settlement visa is a big application. It is advised that you speak to a Global Migrate case worker to ensure that you have filled out the application correctly, and that you have all the evidence required.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Types of settlement visas</strong><br><br>\r\nThough they all grant indefinite leave to remain, there are multiple types of settlement visa. They differ in terms of what information they need, and what you will need to prove.<br><br>\r\nThe SET(M) visa is for people who wish to settle permanently in the UK as a married partner or civil partner of a British citizen or somebody already settled in the UK.<br><br>\r\nSET(O) covers most situations where a person has been in the UK for five years under other types of visa. This includes Tier 1 and Tier 2 visa holders.<br><br>\r\nOther SET visas are available for special cases such as children of settled people, victims of domestic violence, and retirees of independent means.<br><br>\r\nTo find out which category applies to you, contact Global Migrate for an assessment and advice on submitting a successful application.<br><br>\r\n</p> <p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Indefinite Leave to Remain', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '187-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:41:07', '2014-03-07 07:41:07', '', 187, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/187-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(314, 1, '2014-03-07 07:41:13', '2014-03-07 07:41:13', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                 Canada offers a program that allows immigrant investors to move to the country. The Immigrant Investor Program is currently on hold until further notice, although some investor visas are available through the Quebec Immigrant Investor Program.<br><br>\r\nApplications made before 1 July 2012 will still be processed, though. For these applications, you will need to show that you have suitable business experience along with sufficient funds to invest.<br><br>\r\nFor these applications, you will need a net worth of at least C$1,600,000, and make a C$800,000 investment. The investment is administered by Canadian immigration, and is used to improve the economy of the Canadian provinces.<br><br>\r\nOnce the investment is made, you will be granted a permanent residency visa. The original investment is returned to you, without interest, after around five years and three months. The processing time does vary, and Global-Migrate’s Canadian immigration consultants can give you the most up-to-date information.<br><br>\r\nAlthough this visa category is currently on hold, there are plenty of other ways for skilled business people to migrate to Canada. To find out about alternatives to the Investor visa, call, email, or request a call back from Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nWe have years of experience helping people make their Canadian immigration dream a reality. Our free initial assessment can help determine the best visa choice for your individual circumstance. Get in touch today to get started!<br><br>\r\n\r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Investor Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '115-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:41:13', '2014-03-07 07:41:13', '', 115, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/115-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(315, 1, '2014-03-07 07:41:32', '2014-03-07 07:41:32', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n     </p><table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n  <tbody><tr>\r\n    <td width="68%" valign="top">Apply to British language schools without any charge!&#12288;You can even get 10% discount for some schools! For more information, please call or visit our office.\r\n    <h4>Why Us?</h4>\r\n    You can apply to all the language schools in UK without any charge and all of our counsellors can assist you to find the right language school which suits you.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\nAll of the language schools we recommend are certified by the British Council.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThey have created an outstanding network of study centres that cater specifically for the specialist needs of international students.\r\n<h4>Our service</h4>\r\nWe offer you free counselling service as well. Our low-cost service will help you to stay in the UK longer. We do not charge you additional fees. You simply need to pay your tuition fees for the language school you would like to go to.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nPlease contact Global Migrate info@global-migrate.com\r\n<h4>Our Partner</h4>\r\n<img src="images/into.jpg"><br>\r\nDelivery of fully integrated pathway programmes:<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Foundation</li>\r\n<li>Diploma</li>\r\n<li>Graduate Diploma</li>\r\n<li>A Levels (Medicine &amp; Dendistry)</li>\r\n<li>Academic English</li>\r\n<li>General English</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nProgrammes delivered on the partner university campus<br>\r\n	\r\nGuaranteed entry to a wide range of degree courses	<br>\r\n\r\nAccess to university''s first class facilities	<br>\r\n\r\nAccess to comprehensive academic and social support	<br>\r\n\r\nMultiple start dates\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width="32%" valign="top"><table width="100%" cellspacing="10" ce