itle="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Language Schools in the UK', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:41:32', '2014-03-07 07:41:32', '', 258, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(316, 1, '2014-03-07 07:44:06', '2014-03-07 07:44:06', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n               \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				Long-term residents of the United Kingdom may be able to apply for settlement based on this residency. This settlement path, called long residence, granted indefinite leave to remain to migrants who had resided in the UK continuously for 10 or 14 years, depending on the specific circumstances.<br><br>\r\nBecause of changing immigration rules, it is important to speak to a qualified immigration advisor before applying for a long-term residency settlement. Global-Migrate’s advisors are trained and can help you prepare an application based on the current rules.<br><br>\r\nBefore 9 July 2012, long residence was granted after 14 years of continuous residence. If an application was made before that date, it will still be considered under the previous rules.<br><br>\r\nApplications made after 9 July 2012, however, are judged by the new rules. Call Global-Migrate to find out what rules will be used to judge your application, and to get an assessment of your case.<br><br>\r\nThe current immigration rules will allow settlement after 10 years of continuous lawful residence. This means that you will have to have been in the UK for that period of time, and that you did not breach the terms of your visa at any point. You must also meet language and life requirements, as you would for any settlement visa.<br><br>\r\nIf you have been in the UK for 10 years, there is no limit as to when you can apply for settlement. After 10 years you become eligible, and remain eligible. However, your case will be judged by the rules in effect at the time of your application. If you wait to apply, the rules are subject to change.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate helps hundreds of people every year who want to apply for settlement in the United Kingdom. Our team of experienced advisors can help you figure out if your application will be successful. If we believe your application will be successful, we can help you through the entire application process.<br><br>\r\nTo find out more about long term residency, and the current requirements, get in touch with us today.\r\n</p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Long Term Residency', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:44:06', '2014-03-07 07:44:06', '', 193, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/193-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(317, 1, '2014-03-07 07:44:20', '2014-03-07 07:44:20', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				  A Canadian citizen or permanent resident may sponsor their spouse, common-law partner or conjugal partner to move to Canada to live with them.<br><br>\r\nAn application for Family Class sponsorship can be made if your spouse, common-law or conjugal partner  live inside or outside Canada.<br><br>\r\nAll applicants for permanent residence must go through medical, criminal and background screening.<br><br>\r\nTo be eligible for this type of visa, the foreign national and their spouse must be married or in a civil partnership. If you are not yet married, you can apply for a fiancé visa instead. If you aren’t sure what visa you need, request a call back from one of Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nFor a successful application, you’ll need to provide proof of your marriage and relationship. This includes documents like a marriage certificate along with information about how and when you met your spouse.<br><br>\r\nTo be a sponsor, you must be 18 years of age or older.<br><br>\r\nLodging the application for a marriage visa can be stressful, and requires a lot of documentation. Before you start, call Global-Migrate for a free immigration assessment. We can help save you the hassle and expense of a refusal. With a high success rate and excellent customer service, Global-Migrate can take the stress of applying away.<br><br>\r\nPlease call us now on +44 (0) 207 993 4762 to discuss your application or use our free assessment form below and we will be in touch.\r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Marriage Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '109-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:44:20', '2014-03-07 07:44:20', '', 109, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/109-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
