d responding to any questions raised by the immigration authorities.</p>\r\n<p>Written advice regarding any changes made to the immigration laws that may effect your application under the regulations.</p>\r\n<p>Contact us now to discuss which of our services suits your needs best and we shall work with you all the way to help you secure the visa you require. We can be contacted on +44 207 9934762 or alternatively you can email us at info@global-migrate.com</p>\r\n<p>Let&#8217;s get your application approved the first time.<br />\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n            <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:45:09', '2014-03-07 07:45:09', '', 17, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(386, 1, '2014-03-07 13:06:02', '2014-03-07 13:06:02', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Australia has long been a popular immigration destination. The country’s points-based visa system allows certain skilled workers to gain permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Nominated, or subclass 190, Visa.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you are thinking of applying for a Skilled Nominated Visa, get in touch with Global-Migrate today for a free visa assessment. Our qualified advisors can help determine if this is the right visa for you.\r\n\r\n\r\nAs with all of Australia’s skilled worker visas, the subclass 190 visa does have some basic requirements. These include an English language requirement as well as an age requirement. If you’re under 50 and have the language ability, you can submit an expression of interest for a subclass 190 visa.&nbsp;\r\n <a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> </a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLike the other skilled worker visas, you will need to pass the points assessment for the Skilled Nominated visa. To find out about what can earn you points, and how many points you’ll need, speak to Global-Migrate’s MARA registered consultants. We have helped many people with their skilled immigration applications, and can help you with yours.\r\n\r\n\r\nFor the Skilled Nominated visa, you will also need a state or territory nomination. Some states and territories are in need of specific types of skilled workers. If you receive a nomination, you will need to settle in that state or territory. If you want to find out about the benefits, and limits, of a nomination speak to a Global-Migrate representative today.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe subclass 190 visa can be a great way to migrate to Australia. If you qualify, it can give you and your spouse the ability to take up permanent residency in Australia, and can put you on the path to citizenship.\r\n\r\n\r\nOf course, as with any visa application, the Australian subclass 190 visa process can be confusing. Working with an experienced immigration advisor like global-Migrate can help ensure you’re submitting your application correctly. Call us, or request a call back, today.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n</a>\r\n<div class="more"></div></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Skilled &ndash; Nominated (subclass 190) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:06:02', '2014-03-07 13:06:02', '', 51, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(320, 1, '2014-03-07 07:45:41', '2014-03-07 07:45:41', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n               Australia has long been a popular immigration destination. The country’s points-based visa system allows certain skilled workers to gain permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Nominated, or subclass 190, Visa.<br><br>\r\nIf you are thinking of applying for a Skilled Nominated Visa, get in touch with Global-Migrate today for a free visa assessment. Our qualified advisors can help determine if this is the right visa for you.<br><br>\r\nAs with all of Australia’s skilled worker visas, the subclass 190 visa does have some basic requirements. These include an English language requirement as well as an age requirement. If you’re under 50 and have the language ability, you can submit an expression of interest for a subclass 190 visa.<br>\r\n <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> </a></p><div class="more"></div>\r\n <br>\r\nLike the other skilled worker visas, you will need to pass the points assessment for the Skilled Nominated visa. To find out about what can earn you points, and how many points you’ll need, speak to Global-Migrate’s MARA registered consultants. We have helped many people with their skilled immigration applications, and can help you with yours.<br><br>\r\nFor the Skilled Nominated visa, you will also need a state or territory nomination. Some states and territories are in need of specific types of skilled workers. If you receive a nomination, you will need to settle in that state or territory. If you want to find out about the benefits, and limits, of a nomination speak to a Global-Migrate representative today.<br><br>\r\nThe subclass 190 visa can be a great way to migrate to Australia. If you qualify, it can give you and your spouse the ability to take up permanent residency in Australia, and can put you on the path to citizenship.<br><br>\r\nOf course, as with any visa application, the Australian subclass 190 visa process can be confusing. Working with an experienced immigration advisor like global-Migrate can help ensure you’re submitting your application correctly. Call us, or request a call back, today.\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n     ', 'Skilled &ndash; Nominated (subclass 190) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:45:41', '2014-03-07 07:45:41', '', 51, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(321, 1, '2014-03-07 07:45:54', '2014-03-07 07:45:54', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\nSkilled Immigration to Australia is the most common and popular route for highly skilled people. Australia has a history of employing high quality skilled workers, especially from countries like the UK. All skilled workers get rewarded in the form of high salaries, career growth and stability. Workers from different kind of trades, including Carpenters, Plumbers, Welders, Floor tilers, Mechanics, Electricians, IT consultants, Teachers, Accountants migrate to Australia every day, every week, every month. Global Migrate is proud to be a part of their journey.<br><br>\r\nThe three options available for Skilled Immigration to Australia are;\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Skilled Independent Visa - (Subclass 189)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Independent visa is a points-based application. To qualify for the independent visa, you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements, you will be eligible for this visa. This visa is without a doubt the most desired route of immigration to Australia; however, you need to score very high points to be able to apply for this visa. This is an independent application which means no state, or territory will sponsor you and you need to score the required points without having to claim any bonus points for sponsorship.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-189.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated Visa &ndash; (Subclass 190)</h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Sponsored visa is a points-based application. To qualify for this type of visa you must first meet basic requirements around your age, English competence, training and work experience. Once you meet these requirements you may be eligible for this visa. Once approved you become a permanent resident of Australia from day one however you have a restriction to your stay in Australia, where you need to live in the region that sponsors your occupation for at least 24 months.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-190.html">Read More…</a></strong></p>\r\n<h4>Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Visa &ndash; (Subclass 489) </h4>\r\n<p>The Skilled Regional Sponsored visa is initially based on meeting a point score. To qualify for this visa, you must first pass basic requirements. You get points for your age, English competence, training, work experience and having an eligible relative (or a state) able to sponsor you. Once you meet these requirements, you may be eligible for this type of visa. This is initially a 3 year visa sponsored by a state.<br>\r\n<strong><a style="color:#0033CC" href="skilled-subclass-489.html">Read More… </a></strong></p>\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n       ', 'Skilled Immigration Australia', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 07:45:54', '2014-03-07 07:45:54', '', 47, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/47-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(390, 1, '2014-03-07 13:15:53', '2014-03-07 13:15:53', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Australia offers a set of points-based visas for skilled workers from around the world. These visas allow you to migrate to Australia and can give you permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Independent Visa, also known as Subclass 189.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you’re considering a move to Australia, a Skilled Independent Visa might be right for you. To get your free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Skilled Independent Visa has some basic requirements, including an English language requirement and an age limit of 50 years old. To apply for the visa, you will need to submit an expression of interest, in which you provide information about your occupation.\r\n<a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAustralia’s Skilled Occupation List includes details of the types of occupations that are eligible for the subclass 189 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine if your occupation is included in the list. You will also need to have a skill assessment to determine if your skills within that occupation are suitable.\r\n\r\n\r\nAlthough you will need to prove your ability, the Subclass 189 visa can be a great opportunity for you to live and work in Australia. To find out about the requirements for a particular occupation, and to find out how to maximise your chances of getting approved for this type of visa, call Global-Migrate’s MARA regulated advisors.\r\n\r\n\r\nOnce your expression of interest is approved, you’ll be invited to apply for the Skilled Independent Visa. The visa can allow you, and a spouse, to travel freely to Australia for up to five years. If you are interested in applying for this visa, get in touch with us today.\r\n\r\n\r\nWith years of skilled migration experience, Global-Migrate’s consultants are able to help you find the best path for your migration. We offer a free initial assessment that can tell you whether you can qualify for a Subclass 189 visa, so call or email today.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n</a>\r\n<div class="more"></div></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Skilled Independent Subclass 189 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '49-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:15:53', '2014-03-07 13:15:53', '', 49, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/49-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
