ike global-Migrate can help ensure you’re submitting your application correctly. Call us, or request a call back, today.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left"></td>\n<td align="right">\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="10"></td>\n<td width="20"></td>\n<td width="36"></td>\n<td width="34"></td>\n<td width="41"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Skilled &ndash; Nominated (subclass 190) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '51-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:16:33', '2014-03-07 13:16:33', '', 51, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/51-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(391, 1, '2014-03-07 13:19:51', '2014-03-07 13:19:51', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Australia offers skilled workers permanent residency under the points-based visa system. One of these visa types is the Skilled Regional Sponsored, or subclass 489, visa. Like the other visas in this system, you must demonstrate knowledge of the English language, and you must be under 50 years old.\n\nGlobal-Migrate’s MARA regulated immigration advisors have helped many people with their skilled migrant visas. To receive your free visa assessment, get in touch today. We can help determine in the subclass 489 visa is right for you.\n\nTo qualify for this visa, you must also have sponsorship from a relative in Australia. The Skilled Regional visa is aimed at certain Designated Areas of Australia. Your family member must live in one of these areas. To find out what relatives can sponsor you, and where they must live, get in touch with Global-Migrate for the most up-to-date information.\n<a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> </a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\nAlternatively, you can apply on the basis of a nomination from a participating state or territory government. For more information about this path, and how to get a nomination, call Global-Migrate’s advisors today.\n\nOur consultants can also give you guidance about the application process. For the subclass 489 visa, you will need to first submit an expression of interest, in which you will need to give information about your occupation and your skill level. Global-Migrate can help you with your Expression of Interest, and can help you find out about what occupations are in demand in Australia.\n\nThe 489 visa can be a great option for living and working in Australia. While you will need to stay in the specific area of your sponsorship or nomination during the first part of your visa, you will be eligible to apply for permanent residency after two years. When this is granted, you will be free to live and work in any part of Australia.\n\nThe Skilled Nominated or Sponsored Provisional Visa can be the ideal way for you to migrate to Australia. To find out more about this and other visas, and to find out the best choice for you, call Global-Migrate’s experienced advisors today.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left"></td>\n<td align="right">\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="10"></td>\n<td width="20"></td>\n<td width="36"></td>\n<td width="34"></td>\n<td width="41"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Skilled-Nominated or Sponsored (Provisional)-(subclass 489) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '53-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:19:51', '2014-03-07 13:19:51', '', 53, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/53-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(387, 1, '2014-03-07 13:13:16', '2014-03-07 13:13:16', '            <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n               \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2">\r\n                  <p>\r\n                Australia offers a set of points-based visas for skilled workers from around the world. These visas allow you to migrate to Australia and can give you permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Independent Visa, also known as Subclass 189.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re considering a move to Australia, a Skilled Independent Visa might be right for you. To get your free visa assessment, get in touch with Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nThe Skilled Independent Visa has some basic requirements, including an English language requirement and an age limit of 50 years old. To apply for the visa, you will need to submit an expression of interest, in which you provide information about your occupation.<br>\r\n<a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"></a></p>\r\n<br>\r\nAustralia’s Skilled Occupation List includes details of the types of occupations that are eligible for the subclass 189 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine if your occupation is included in the list. You will also need to have a skill assessment to determine if your skills within that occupation are suitable.<br><br>\r\nAlthough you will need to prove your ability, the Subclass 189 visa can be a great opportunity for you to live and work in Australia. To find out about the requirements for a particular occupation, and to find out how to maximise your chances of getting approved for this type of visa, call Global-Migrate’s MARA regulated advisors.<br><br>\r\nOnce your expression of interest is approved, you’ll be invited to apply for the Skilled Independent Visa. The visa can allow you, and a spouse, to travel freely to Australia for up to five years. If you are interested in applying for this visa, get in touch with us today.<br><br>\r\nWith years of skilled migration experience, Global-Migrate’s consultants are able to help you find the best path for your migration. We offer a free initial assessment that can tell you whether you can qualify for a Subclass 189 visa, so call or email today.\r\n\r\n                  <p></p> </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n              <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n  ', 'Skilled Independent Subclass 189 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '49-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:13:16', '2014-03-07 13:13:16', '', 49, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/49-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(388, 1, '2014-03-07 13:14:42', '2014-03-07 13:14:42', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Australia has long been a popular immigration destination. The country’s points-based visa system allows certain skilled workers to gain permanent residency. One of the visas in this program is the Skilled Nominated, or subclass 190, Visa.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you are thinking of applying for a Skilled Nominated Visa, get in touch with Global-Migrate today for a free visa assessment. Our qualified advisors can help determine if this is the right visa for you.\r\n\r\n\r\nAs with all of Australia’s skilled worker visas, the subclass 190 visa does have some basic requirements. These include an English language requirement as well as an age requirement. If you’re under 50 and have the language ability, you can submit an expression of interest for a subclass 190 visa.&nbsp;\r\n <a class="more" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"> </a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLike the other skilled worker visas, you will need to pass the points assessment for the Skilled Nominated visa. To find out about what can earn you points, and how many points you’ll need, speak to Global-Migrate’s MARA registered consultants. We have helped many people with their skilled immigration applications, and can help you with yours.\r\n\r\n\r\nFor the Skilled Nominated visa, you will also need a state or territory nomination. Some states and territories are in need of specific types of skilled workers. If you receive a nomination, you will need to settle in that state or territory. If you want to find out about the benefits, and limits, of a nomination speak to a Global-Migrate representative today.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe subclass 190 visa can be a great way to migrate to Australia. If you qualify, it can give you and your spouse the ability to take up permanent residency in Australia, and can put you on the path to citizenship.\r\n\r\n\r\nOf course, as with any visa application, the Australian subclass 190 visa process can be confusing. Working with an experienced immigration advisor like global-Migrate can help ensure you’re submitting your application correctly. Call us, or request a call back, today.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php">\r\n<div class="more"></div></a></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Skilled &ndash; Nominated (subclass 190) Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:14:42', '2014-03-07 13:14:42', '', 51, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
