(409, 1, '2014-03-07 13:59:51', '2014-03-07 13:59:51', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				 </p><p>The United Kingdom is a popular place, with people wishing to immigrate for all sorts of reasons. At Global-Migrate, we help people make their immigration dreams come true. We have worked on thousands of cases, and our high success rate has established us as the most trusted name in the UK immigration industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Reasons for immigration</h4>\r\n<p>There are lots of reasons why you might want to immigrate to the UK, and the UK has different visas for each reason. Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors can help you determine which visa category you should apply for, and can assess whether you’ll qualify for a visa.<br><br>\r\nEach type of visa has its own rules and regulations, and Global-Migrate can help you make a successful application. To avoid a rejection, you want to be certain you have done everything right and provided all the necessary information.<br><br>\r\n</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n\r\n<p></p><h4>Complicated process made easy</h4>\r\nImmigration rules change regularly, though, so it’s important to keep up to date. If this seems overwhelming, don’t worry. That’s what Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors are here for. We’ll help make the immigration process straightforward and successful for you.<br><br>\r\nThe visa application process can be complicated. We train our advisors and senior case workers to be able to deal with even the more difficult cases. We’re committed to our clients’ success and are able to help with your application, regardless of how complicated it might be.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a><p></p>\r\n<h4>Types of Visa</h4>\r\nUK visas fall into several categories. They each have more than one type of visa within them, and each visa has its own requirements.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Family visas:</strong> These include fiancé visas, marriage visas, and family dependent visas. They generally cover situations where you’re going to the UK to be with your family.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Settlement and Naturalisation:</strong> This are the steps you take to stay in the UK permanently, either as a British citizen or not.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Working visas:</strong> These visas are part of the points-based system and cover situations in which you’re coming to the UK to take up work. </li>\r\n<li><strong>Student visas:</strong> These visas are another part of the points-based system and allow you to come to the UK to study at an approved academic institution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a>\r\n\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left"> </td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Immigration - Global Migrate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 13:59:51', '2014-03-07 13:59:51', '', 133, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/133-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(419, 1, '2014-03-07 14:18:46', '2014-03-07 14:18:46', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n				  Anyone with the Right of Abode has no restrictions to live and work in the UK. They can enter and leave the UK without any immigration restrictions.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAll British citizens have the right of abode in the United Kingdom.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSome Commonwealth citizens also have the right of abode.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you wish to claim the right of abode, you must prove it by producing:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n<li>a United Kingdom passport describing you as a British citizen or a British subject with the right of abode</li>\r\n<li>a United Kingdom identity card describing you as a British citizen or a British subject with the right of abode</li>\r\n<li>a certificate of entitlement to the right of abode in the United Kingdom that has been issued by the Government of the United Kingdom or on its behalf.\r\n</li></ul>\r\nIf you are not a British Citizen that’s ok. You may still have the Right of Abode if, on 31 December 1982, you were:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>a Commonwealth citizen with a parent who, at the time of your birth or legal adoption, was a citizen of the United Kingdom and Colonies because he/she was born in the United Kingdom</li>\r\n<li>a female Commonwealth citizen who was, or had been, married to a man who had the right of abode. You must have been married to him before 1 January 1983.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNational’s of certain countries do not have the Right of Abode as there countries left the Commonwealth before 1983 and joined it again afterwards. South Africa and Pakistan are an example of such countries.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSuch applications can be complex and may require professional assistance as it may not be easy to convince the UK government that you genuinely have the Right of Abode. These applications require a lot of documents as well and need to be submitted in the right order.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate is a leading UK immigration consultancy. We help hundreds of client’s every year who are interested in UK citizenship, a work visa and even a temporary visa. Global-Migrate’s consulants will guide you to the best UK visa which meets your requirement.\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate has fully qualified and trained UK visas specialists. This allows us to provide our client’s with a service second to none. Our rate of success continues to grow every day and with our help you could soon be lodging a strong application. To enquire about how to become a British Citizen why don’t you use our Free assessment tool. <p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Right of Abode', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '195-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:18:46', '2014-03-07 14:18:46', '', 195, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/195-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
