(422, 1, '2014-03-07 14:22:04', '2014-03-07 14:22:04', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n                \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\n                  The UK is a top destination for foreign study and offers some of the world’s most recognised and valued qualifications. It can be stressful to migrate to the UK for study, though, which is where we come in. We work with the top UK universities and UKBA approved colleges to help students relocate, and have done for the past 15 years.<br>\n<br>\n\nThe UK is the second most popular destination, after the US, for student visas, and more than 3,000 institutions welcome international undergraduates and graduates.\n<br>\n<br>\n\nTo successfully receive a UK Tier 4 student visa, and a university place, you may be asked to sit an English Language Test. The most common are IELTS or TOEFL tests. These assess you to see whether you would learn effectively in an English institution. The IELTS is organised by the British Council. Results take two to three weeks and the minimum scores are usually 6.0 for the IELTS and 550 for the TOEFL.\n<br>\n<br>\n\nFor certain post-graduate studies you will need a good GMAT score (Graduate Management Admission Test). This is in addition to the IELTS/TOEFL scores and you also need two to three years’ work experience, as well as a fair academic performance in your original degree.\n<br>\n<br>\n\nUndergraduate courses cost approximately £7,000 for Arts, £8,000 for Sciences and between £7,000 and £18,000 for medial programmes. Universities do set their own fees, though, which vary per subject and institution. For postgraduate study you should budget for a 12-month academic year.\nInternational students staying in the UK for six months or more qualify for free National Health Service (NHS) care as well. Those staying for a shorter period of time can get an EU healthcare card to prove eligibility for treatment and arrange payment at a later date.\n</p><h4>Eligibility </h4>\nAdult students applying to study in the UK must have recognised qualifications equivalent to the National Qualification Framework (NQF) in the UK education system. They must also produce evidence they have sufficient funds to meet the maintenance requirement and the documents used to get a university or college offer initially.\n<br>\n<br>\n\nA visa letter from the education provider is most important in the points-based assessment process, while showing proof of maintenance funds to cover course fees and living expenses will also contribute to the points tally.\n<br>\n<br>\n\nFor more assistance with the involved task of moving to study please use our FREE online assessment tool. Our top professionals can help you with every aspect of migrating in a friendly and hassle-free manner.\n                   <p></p></td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'UK Study Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:22:04', '2014-03-07 14:22:04', '', 149, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/149-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(423, 1, '2014-03-07 14:22:52', '2014-03-07 14:22:52', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n              \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p> \r\n				  This application is for people who are resident outside the United Kingdom. This visa is for someone who is a sponsored young person of a certain age, and nationality (see below) wishing to experience life in the United Kingdom (UK) under Tier 5 (Youth Mobility Scheme) of the points based system. Your government acts as sponsor.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe Youth Mobility Scheme is only available to people resident outside the UK.\r\n<br>\r\n</p><h4>Which countries are participating in the Youth Mobility Scheme (YMS)?</h4>\r\nSo far, only Australia, Canada, Japan, Monaco and New Zealand have joined the YMS. However, you are also eligible to apply if you are a British Overseas Citizen, British Overseas Territories Citizen or a British National (Overseas).\r\n<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate has helped many clients in obtaining a successful application. We specialise in the Youth Mobility Scheme visas and would love to answer any questions you may have. Please call us on +44 (0) 207 9934762 for more information.<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Tier 5 Temporary Worker Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '183-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:22:52', '2014-03-07 14:22:52', '', 183, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(424, 1, '2014-03-07 14:24:15', '2014-03-07 14:24:15', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                  The UK is a top destination for foreign study and offers some of the world’s most recognised and valued qualifications. It can be stressful to migrate to the UK for study, though, which is where we come in. We work with the top UK universities and UKBA approved colleges to help students relocate, and have done for the past 15 years.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThe UK is the second most popular destination, after the US, for student visas, and more than 3,000 institutions welcome international undergraduates and graduates.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nTo successfully receive a UK Tier 4 student visa, and a university place, you may be asked to sit an English Language Test. The most common are IELTS or TOEFL tests. These assess you to see whether you would learn effectively in an English institution. The IELTS is organised by the British Council. Results take two to three weeks and the minimum scores are usually 6.0 for the IELTS and 550 for the TOEFL.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFor certain post-graduate studies you will need a good GMAT score (Graduate Management Admission Test). This is in addition to the IELTS/TOEFL scores and you also need two to three years’ work experience, as well as a fair academic performance in your original degree.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nUndergraduate courses cost approximately £7,000 for Arts, £8,000 for Sciences and between £7,000 and £18,000 for medial programmes. Universities do set their own fees, though, which vary per subject and institution. For postgraduate study you should budget for a 12-month academic year.\r\nInternational students staying in the UK for six months or more qualify for free National Health Service (NHS) care as well. Those staying for a shorter period of time can get an EU healthcare card to prove eligibility for treatment and arrange payment at a later date.\r\n</p><h4>Eligibility </h4>\r\nAdult students applying to study in the UK must have recognised qualifications equivalent to the National Qualification Framework (NQF) in the UK education system. They must also produce evidence they have sufficient funds to meet the maintenance requirement and the documents used to get a university or college offer initially.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nA visa letter from the education provider is most important in the points-based assessment process, while showing proof of maintenance funds to cover course fees and living expenses will also contribute to the points tally.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFor more assistance with the involved task of moving to study please use our FREE online assessment tool. Our top professionals can help you with every aspect of migrating in a friendly and hassle-free manner.\r\n                   <p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Study Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:24:15', '2014-03-07 14:24:15', '', 149, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/149-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(425, 1, '2014-03-07 14:28:16', '2014-03-07 14:28:16', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n                \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>Welcome to Global Migrate Visas, the world''s leading UK immigration experts.  We offer a unique team of UK immigration lawyers, former immigration officers and experienced immigration specialists to ensure our clients receive the best advice from people who care.\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src="images/img-uk.jpg">\nThere are a wide range of UK visas on offer, each with different rules and expectations. It can be tricky to understand which bracket you fall in as an individual, which is where our expert help and advice becomes useful. With our professional and qualified UK immigration experts, you can resolve the complicated issue of a UK visa in no time. Feel free to use our FREE assessment tool to determine which Visa is relevant to you, or alternatively follow the links and read in further depth. </p>\n<a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\n&nbsp;\n<p>\nEconomic migration is a key factor in UK immigration policy, and permitting skilled immigration to the UK brings the necessary skills and experience for economic growth. For corporate inquiries, please visit our corporate services page to see how we can assist your company.\n<br><br>\n\nThe UK visas are divided into five tiers, each with a specific purpose.\n</p><h4>Tier One - UK Visas for Highly Skilled Migrants</h4>\nIf you have a professional trade which may benefit the UK (such as a GP or a teacher) then you may have enough education points to qualify for permanent residency in the UK.\n<h4>Tier Two - UK Visas for Medium and Highly Skilled Workers</h4>\nYou can apply for this UK visa application if you have received an offer of employment by a UK company which is based in Britain.\n<h4>Tier Five - Short Term Workers</h4>\nThis UK visa application will allow short term workers to work in the UK on a temporary basis. Anyone between the ages of 18 to 30 can apply through this UK visa application as part of the ''Youth Mobility Scheme'' which will allow young people to live and work in the country on a working holiday.\n<h4>Other UK Immigration Solutions</h4>\nThe UK also offers the Post Study Work Programme, which is similar to Tiers 4 and 5. If you are seeking a Family Based Visa please follow the links to the Marriage Visa, Fiancé Visa, Ancestry Visa and De Facto Visa pages.\n<p></p>\n</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10"> </td> \n            <td width="20"> </td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'UK Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '135-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:28:16', '2014-03-07 14:28:16', '', 135, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/135-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(426, 1, '2014-03-07 14:28:34', '2014-03-07 14:28:34', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>Welcome to Global Migrate Visas, the world''s leading UK immigration experts.  We offer a unique team of UK immigration lawyers, former immigration officers and experienced immigration specialists to ensure our clients receive the best advice from people who care.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src="images/img-uk.jpg">\r\nThere are a wide range of UK visas on offer, each with different rules and expectations. It can be tricky to understand which bracket you fall in as an individual, which is where our expert help and advice becomes useful. With our professional and qualified UK immigration experts, you can resolve the complicated issue of a UK visa in no time. Feel free to use our FREE assessment tool to determine which Visa is relevant to you, or alternatively follow the links and read in further depth. </p>\r\n<a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\r\nEconomic migration is a key factor in UK immigration policy, and permitting skilled immigration to the UK brings the necessary skills and experience for economic growth. For corporate inquiries, please visit our corporate services page to see how we can assist your company.\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nThe UK visas are divided into five tiers, each with a specific purpose.\r\n</p><h4>Tier One - UK Visas for Highly Skilled Migrants</h4>\r\nIf you have a professional trade which may benefit the UK (such as a GP or a teacher) then you may have enough education points to qualify for permanent residency in the UK.\r\n<h4>Tier Two - UK Visas for Medium and Highly Skilled Workers</h4>\r\nYou can apply for this UK visa application if you have received an offer of employment by a UK company which is based in Britain.\r\n<h4>Tier Five - Short Term Workers</h4>\r\nThis UK visa application will allow short term workers to work in the UK on a temporary basis. Anyone between the ages of 18 to 30 can apply through this UK visa application as part of the ''Youth Mobility Scheme'' which will allow young people to live and work in the country on a working holiday.\r\n<h4>Other UK Immigration Solutions</h4>\r\nThe UK also offers the Post Study Work Programme, which is similar to Tiers 4 and 5. If you are seeking a Family Based Visa please follow the links to the Marriage Visa, Fiancé Visa, Ancestry Visa and De Facto Visa pages.\r\n<p></p>\r\n</td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '135-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:28:34', '2014-03-07 14:28:34', '', 135, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/135-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(427, 1, '2014-03-07 14:28:49', '2014-03-07 14:28:49', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>If you are in the United Kingdom on a visa, you might be able to extend your stay. The application for an extension is often slightly different than for the original visa. However, you will still need to provide proof that you are eligible to be in the UK.<br><br>\r\nAt Global-Migrate, we have helped thousands of people extend their visa. To find out how we can help with your visa extension, call us today.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 1 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend your stay on a Tier 1 visa, you will need to provide the same evidence that you did when you applied for your initial visa. Depending on which category of Tier 1 visa you hold, the rules for extensions have changed recently. Our visa assessment can help determine what extension options are available to you.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 2 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend a Tier 2 visa, your employer will need to submit the application. In most cases, your initial visa will have been for 5 years, after which time you can apply for a settlement, or indefinite leave to remain, visa. If your visa was for less than 5 years, or you do not want to apply for settlement, you may be able to extend your Tier 2 visa. Global-Migrate can help you determine how best to extend your Tier 2 stay.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Tier 4 Extensions</strong><br><br>\r\nTo extend your Tier 4 visa, you will need to show that you are still enrolled at your academic institution. While your initial visa is granted for the entire time of your course, you might need to extend your stay if it is taking you longer to complete your course. If you have been accepted into another course, such as for a postgraduate degree, you might be able to apply for an extension from within the UK. Global-Migrate’s advisors can help determine your Tier 4 extension options.<br><br>\r\n<strong>Other categories</strong><br><br>\r\nIf you are in the UK on any other type of visa, you may still be able to extend your stay. Call Global-Migrate today to discuss visa extensions and transfers. We’re committed to the highest levels of customer service and pride ourselves in being able to help all of our clients with their immigration dreams.<br><br>\r\n</p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK Visa Extensions &ndash; Extend UK Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '191-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:28:49', '2014-03-07 14:28:49', '', 191, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/191-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(428, 1, '2014-03-07 14:31:42', '2014-03-07 14:31:42', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n                \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>The UK Marriage Visa, also known as a spouse visa or FLR(M), allows foreign nationals from outside the EEA to settle in the UK with a husband, wife, or civil partner. The spouse of the foreign national must already be settled in the UK, either as a British national or as a permanent resident.<br><br>\nTo be eligible for this type of visa, the foreign national and their spouse must be married or in a civil partnership. If you are not yet married, you can apply for a fiancé visa instead. If you aren’t sure what visa you need, request a call back from one of Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors.<br><br>\nFor a successful application, you’ll need to provide proof of your marriage and relationship. This includes documents like a marriage certificate along with information about how and when you met your spouse.<br><br>\n <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\n&nbsp;</p><div class="more"></div><br>\nYou will also need to prove that you can afford to support yourself and your dependents without any government assistance. Global-Migrate’s advisors can help you determine the actual amount of income you will need to have, and how you will need to prove this.<br><br>\nAlong with this, you’ll need to demonstrate that you know English, and that you are a suitable candidate for a visa. Immigration officers will look at things like past visa refusals, so if you have been refused a visa in the past, it is important that you are able to explain this in your application. If you have had a refusal, we strongly advise that you speak to one of our case workers before you apply.<br><br>\nFiling the application for a marriage visa can be stressful, and requires a lot of documentation. Before you start, call Global-Migrate for a free immigration assessment. We can help save you the hassle and expense of a refusal. With a high success rate and excellent customer service, Global-Migrate can take the stress of applying away.<br><br>\n<p></p></td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment" href="free-assessment.php"> <div class="more"></div></a></td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10"> </td> \n            <td width="20"> </td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'UK&nbsp;Marriage Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '159-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:31:42', '2014-03-07 14:31:42', '', 159, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/159-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(429, 1, '2014-03-07 14:31:57', '2014-03-07 14:31:57', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>The UK Marriage Visa, also known as a spouse visa or FLR(M), allows foreign nationals from outside the EEA to settle in the UK with a husband, wife, or civil partner. The spouse of the foreign national must already be settled in the UK, either as a British national or as a permanent resident.<br><br>\r\nTo be eligible for this type of visa, the foreign national and their spouse must be married or in a civil partnership. If you are not yet married, you can apply for a fiancé visa instead. If you aren’t sure what visa you need, request a call back from one of Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nFor a successful application, you’ll need to provide proof of your marriage and relationship. This includes documents like a marriage certificate along with information about how and when you met your spouse.<br><br>\r\n <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n&nbsp;</p><br>\r\nYou will also need to prove that you can afford to support yourself and your dependents without any government assistance. Global-Migrate’s advisors can help you determine the actual amount of income you will need to have, and how you will need to prove this.<br><br>\r\nAlong with this, you’ll need to demonstrate that you know English, and that you are a suitable candidate for a visa. Immigration officers will look at things like past visa refusals, so if you have been refused a visa in the past, it is important that you are able to explain this in your application. If you have had a refusal, we strongly advise that you speak to one of our case workers before you apply.<br><br>\r\nFiling the application for a marriage visa can be stressful, and requires a lot of documentation. Before you start, call Global-Migrate for a free immigration assessment. We can help save you the hassle and expense of a refusal. With a high success rate and excellent customer service, Global-Migrate can take the stress of applying away.<br><br>\r\n<p></p></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10"> </td> \r\n            <td width="20"> </td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'UK&nbsp;Marriage Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:31:57', '2014-03-07 14:31:57', '', 159, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(430, 1, '2014-03-07 14:35:50', '2014-03-07 14:35:50', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n             If you want to temporarily work in the United States, you might be able to apply for a B-1 visa in lieu of an H-1B visa. While the H-1B visas are limited each year, B-1 visas are not. This can make the B-1 in lieu of H-1B option very attractive. To find out if this is right for you, call Global-Migrate’s immigration advisors today.<br><br>\r\nH-1B visas are intended for foreign nationals working for American employers, while the B-1 visa is intended for business visitors to the United States. Unlike H-1B visa holders, B-1 visa holders cannot have any income from a US company, with the exception of certain expenses.<br><br>\r\nTo apply for a B-1 visa in lieu of an H-1B, you must meet certain criteria. These include a minimum of a degree equivalent to a US bachelor’s degree, and the intent to perform work at the level required for an H-1B visa.<br><br>\r\nThe visa application process can be complicated, particularly as you’ll need to prove that you do not intend to stay past the end of your visa, and that you will not be taking on employment with a US company. Speaking to one of Global-Migrate’strained consultants can help you with this difficult and confusing process.<br><br>\r\nIt is important to remember that there will be limits on what you can do during your stay in the US on a B-1 in lieu of H-1B visa. If you want to stay for a longer period of time, work for an American employer, or find out how you can bring your family with you, speak to Global-Migrate about other US visa options.<br><br>\r\nWorking in the United States can be a great experience for you. If you are considering applying for a B-1 in lieu of H-1B, or any other type of visa, call Global-Migrate or request a call back from us today.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA B1 in lieu of H1B', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '203-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:35:50', '2014-03-07 14:35:50', '', 203, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/203-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(432, 1, '2014-03-07 14:36:12', '2014-03-07 14:36:12', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n             If you’re planning to travel to the United States, you’ll need the appropriate visa. For business travellers, this is the B-1 visa. This visa will allow you to take part in certain aspects of business, but does have limits on what you can do while in the US.<br><br>\r\nNationals of some countries may not need to apply for a visa in advance. The Visa Waiver Program allows for this free travel, but is not available for everyone. If you want to check your eligibility for the Visa Waiver Program, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s immigration advisors today.<br><br>\r\nBusiness travel can mean a variety of things. Whether you are travelling to America to attend a meeting or conference, negotiate a deal, or participate in a work-related training program. A B-1 visa does not allow you to take on employment, though.<br><br>\r\nIf you are looking to migrate to the US to work, you will need a different type of visa. To find out about working visa options, contact Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nAs part of your B-1 visa application, you will need to demonstrate that your stay in the US is temporary. In order to prove this, you will have to show that you have significant ties outside of the US, that you have sufficient funds for your travel, and that you have plans to leave the US.<br><br>\r\nWhen you apply, you will also need to attend an embassy interview. Global-Migrate can help you prepare for this interview, and can help you with all the parts of your application. If you represent a company that needs visas for multiple employees, we are able to give you advice about what the US Business Visa Center or Embassy Business Facilitation services can provide.<br><br>\r\nThe United States is full of business opportunities, and travelling to America can help you in your career. Global-Migrate’s team of immigration advisors are qualified to help you with your B-1 visa application. Call us, or request a call back, to find out more.\r\n\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA B1 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '205-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:36:12', '2014-03-07 14:36:12', '', 205, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/205-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(434, 1, '2014-03-07 14:36:23', '2014-03-07 14:36:23', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n               \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\n         If you are planning a trip to the United States for pleasure, tourism, or medical treatment, you’ll need a B-2 Visa. This must be the main purpose of your travel, and there are limits on what you can do during your stay.<br><br>\nIt is also worth noting that nationals from some countries might be able to take advantage of the Visa Waiver Program. If you aren’t sure whether your country is part of the Visa Waiver Program, or if you aren’t eligible for it, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s immigration experts. We can help you determine what visa will be required for your visit to the United States.<br><br>\nTo be approved for a B-2 visa, you will need to prove that you do not intend to immigrate to the US during your travels. In order to prove this, you will need to show things like your ability to pay for your time in the US, your ties to a non-US location, including a job, family, and home, and your return travel.<br><br>\nThe evidence you provide will help the immigration officials process your visa application. Global-Migrate can help you prepare your application, including the embassy interview, which can improve your chance of success.<br><br>\nOnce your B-2 visa is approved, you will be able to enter the United States. While there, though, you will not be able to take on work, or study towards a degree. To find out about the special visas for these or other purposes, speak to a Global-Migrate advisor.<br><br>\nThe United States has many things to offer visitors, and getting a B-2 visa can allow you to enjoy everything the country is famous for. Whether you’re planning travel to the skyscrapers of New York, the beaches of California, or someplace in between, speak to one of Global-Migrate’s qualified advisors today to help make your American travel dreams come true.\n\n\n                     </p>\n                   </td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\n</td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'USA B2 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '207-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:36:23', '2014-03-07 14:36:23', '', 207, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/207-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(435, 1, '2014-03-07 14:36:32', '2014-03-07 14:36:32', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n               \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n         If you are planning a trip to the United States for pleasure, tourism, or medical treatment, you’ll need a B-2 Visa. This must be the main purpose of your travel, and there are limits on what you can do during your stay.<br><br>\r\nIt is also worth noting that nationals from some countries might be able to take advantage of the Visa Waiver Program. If you aren’t sure whether your country is part of the Visa Waiver Program, or if you aren’t eligible for it, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s immigration experts. We can help you determine what visa will be required for your visit to the United States.<br><br>\r\nTo be approved for a B-2 visa, you will need to prove that you do not intend to immigrate to the US during your travels. In order to prove this, you will need to show things like your ability to pay for your time in the US, your ties to a non-US location, including a job, family, and home, and your return travel.<br><br>\r\nThe evidence you provide will help the immigration officials process your visa application. Global-Migrate can help you prepare your application, including the embassy interview, which can improve your chance of success.<br><br>\r\nOnce your B-2 visa is approved, you will be able to enter the United States. While there, though, you will not be able to take on work, or study towards a degree. To find out about the special visas for these or other purposes, speak to a Global-Migrate advisor.<br><br>\r\nThe United States has many things to offer visitors, and getting a B-2 visa can allow you to enjoy everything the country is famous for. Whether you’re planning travel to the skyscrapers of New York, the beaches of California, or someplace in between, speak to one of Global-Migrate’s qualified advisors today to help make your American travel dreams come true.\r\n\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA B2 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '207-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:36:32', '2014-03-07 14:36:32', '', 207, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/207-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(436, 1, '2014-03-07 14:38:45', '2014-03-07 14:38:45', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n               \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n        One of the most popular ways to immigrate to the United States is through one of the employment-based visas. The employment-based visas are limited to approximately 140,000 per year, and are split into five categories. Around 40,000 of these visas are given to those in the Second Preference, or E2, category. This type of visa is for those who hold advanced degrees or have exceptional abilities.<br><br>\r\nFor US immigration, a professional holding an advanced degree requires that you hold a degree beyond a baccalaureate degree. You may also qualify if you have a baccalaureate degree and at least five years of experience in your field. If you don’t meet this qualification, you may still be eligible for a different visa category. To ensure that you’re applying for the right type of visa, call our trained immigration advisors today.<br><br>\r\nA person of exceptional ability can also apply for an E2 visa. If you are a professional with expertise in your field beyond that ordinarily encountered, you might qualify. This can be in the sciences, arts, or business.<br><br>\r\nWith so many people applying for a limited number of visas, it is important to speak to a qualified immigration advisor. Global-Migrate can offer you a free immigration assessment to help determine if an E2 visa is right for you.<br><br>\r\nTo qualify for an E2 visa, you will generally need to have a labour certification as well as a job offer. Your US employer must file a petition on your behalf. If you don’t have these, you can apply for an exemption, though you will have to demonstrate that your migration would be in the national interest.<br><br>\r\nFor more details about these requirements, or how to get an exemption, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s team of qualified immigration advisors today. Our consultants can help you make your immigration dream a reality.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA E2 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '209-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:38:45', '2014-03-07 14:38:45', '', 209, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/209-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(437, 1, '2014-03-07 14:38:58', '2014-03-07 14:38:58', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n      If you are an investor, you might be able to immigrate to the United States through the EB-5 type of visa. This visa is part of the Employment-Based Immigration category, and is also known as the Employment Fifth Preference. To find out more about this category and get a free visa assessment, call or email Global-Migrate today.<br><br>\r\nThe EB-5 is a visa for Immigrant Investors. It is designed to allow for capital investment in the United States. The goal of this visa is to encourage investment in new commercial enterprises that will create jobs in the US.<br><br>\r\nThese visas are extremely limited, with less than 10,000 available each year. Unlike many other employment based categories, the immigrant investor visa does not require a labour certification.<br><br>\r\nThe EB-5 visa can be a difficult application, so it is important to get high quality advice from trained immigration professionals. Global-Migrate can give you a free visa assessment to help determine the best way to make your US immigration dreams come true.<br><br>\r\nAn Immigrant Investor visa can be a great way for you to migrate to the United States and be a valuable part of the American economy. The visa category is divided into four sub-categories. These are used to determine specific requirements, such as how much money you will need to have available for investment.In general, you will need to be able to invest at least $1,000,000 without borrowing. The amount is lower in some circumstances, such as when you will be investing in a high-unemployment area.<br><br>\r\nIf you qualify for an EB-5 visa, you may be able to have your spouse and certain family members join you in the United States. To find out more about the requirements for your family members, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s advisors today.\r\n\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA EB5 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '211-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:38:58', '2014-03-07 14:38:58', '', 211, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/211-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(438, 1, '2014-03-07 14:39:16', '2014-03-07 14:39:16', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n              <tbody>\n                \n                <tr>\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\n              If you are the spouse, parent, or child of an American citizen, you may be able to join them in the United States. For this, you will need one of the types of US visa that are specifically intended for family members. Even within this category, there are many types of visa.<br><br>\nApplying for a US family visa can be a confusing and complex process. You might be unsure about where to start, of you might have a question along the way. In either case, you can call Global-Migrate’s team of qualified immigration advisors for help.<br><br>\nWith most types of US family visas, you will be given permanent residency, or you will be able to apply for permanent residency after your arrival in the US.\n</p><h4>Spouses and fiancés</h4>\nIf you are married to, or engaged to, a US citizen, you can apply for a visa on this basis. If your spouse is a US permanent resident, you might also be eligible to migrate to the US on a family-based visa, too. In most cases, you will need to provide proof of your relationship, undergo a medical examination, and have an interview before you can be granted your visa. Global-Migrate can help you with each step of the process, so call today.\n<h4>Children and parents</h4>\nIf you are the parent or child of a United States citizen, or permanent resident, you might be able to migrate to the US to join them. These visas are also used by US citizens adopting a foreign national. The application will require your US relative to file a petition on your behalf. You and your sponsor will need to prove your family relationship. Global-Migrate can give you details on what sort of proof will be required, as well as the details of the immigration process.<br><br>\nWhatever your family relationship, Global-Migrate can help you find the right visa for your situation. Call us or request a call back today to get your free assessment and other visa help.\n\n                     <p></p>\n                   </td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\n&nbsp;</td>\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\n          <tbody><tr>\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\n            <td width="36"></td>\n            <td width="34"></td>\n            <td width="41"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>', 'USA Family Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '201-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:39:16', '2014-03-07 14:39:16', '', 201, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/201-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
