 right visa for you.<br><br>\r\nThe H-1B visa process can be complicated, so it is helpful to speak to an immigration advisor before starting. To receive a free visa assessment, email or call Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA H1B Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '214-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:40:51', '2014-03-07 14:40:51', '', 214, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/214-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(442, 1, '2014-03-07 14:43:07', '2014-03-07 14:43:07', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n   If you are the fiancé of a United States citizen, you can apply for a US Fiance Visa, also known as a K-1 Visa. This visa will allow you to enter the United States up to 90 days before you get married. After your marriage, you will be able to apply for permanent residency.<br><br>\r\nWhile you will have certain limitations on what you can do during the period before your marriage, permanent residency gives you many benefits. With permanent residency, you will be able to live and work in the United States.<br><br>\r\nGlobal-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors can help you determine if the K-1 Visa is right for you. To begin, try our free visa assessment or call us today.<br><br>\r\nThe first step in the K-1 Visa application is for your American fiancé to file a petition on your behalf. Along with a medical examination, you will also need to provide evidence of your relationship. This includes showing that you and your fiancé have met in person within the past two years.<br><br>\r\nThere are some exceptions to this, though. If you need advice about what documentation you’ll need to provide for your fiancé visa, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s qualified immigration consultants.<br><br>\r\nIf you are applying for a K-1 visa, your children might also be eligible to come to the United States with you. To find out about what type of visa they will require, speak to one of our advisors. Global-Migrate can also help you with other parts of your visa application, too.<br><br>\r\nThe United States is a popular immigration destination, and US visa applications can be complicated and confusing. To ensure your success, our immigration consultants can help you with the entire process. As experienced immigration advisors, we have helped many people turn their immigration dream into a reality.<br><br>\r\nCall us today, or request a call back, and take the first step in joining your American fiancé in the United States.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA K1 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '216-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:43:07', '2014-03-07 14:43:07', '', 216, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/216-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(443, 1, '2014-03-07 14:43:37', '2014-03-07 14:43:37', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n  If you are the husband or wife of an American citizen, you might be able to join them in the United States before your immigration petition is processed. The K-3 visa allows you to enter the United States as a non-immigrant spouse.<br><br>\r\nAs with any immigration process, the application for a K-3 visa can be confusing and complicated. If you are uncertain about any part of the process, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors.<br><br>\r\nTo be eligible for a K-3 visa, you must be legally married to a United States citizen. They must also first file a Petition for Alien Relative, also known as a Form I-130. However, with the K-3 visa, you will be able to enter the US for up to two years while this petition is being processed.<br><br>\r\nFor immigration purposes, only married couples are considered spouses. This does not include same-sex marriages, and many common law marriages. If you are unsure whether you can be considered a spouse for US immigration, speak to one of Global-Migrate’s trained immigration advisors today.<br><br>\r\nIf you are granted a K-3 visa, you will be able to join your American spouse in the United States. You’ll also be eligible to take on employment, and can apply for permanent residency. There are certain limits on your stay, though, so speak to a qualified immigration advisor to find out more details.<br><br>\r\nFor couples married outside the United States, the K-3 visa application must be made from the country where the marriage took place. If you are unsure about where you need to be when you apply, Global-Migrate’s advisors can help you. A K-3 visa holder can also apply for eligible children to join them. To find out more about visas for the children of K-3 holders, speak to a global-Migrate consultant today.<br><br>\r\nThe K-3 visa can be a great way for you to join your American husband or wife in their country. To check whether this is the right visa for you, get your free visa assessment from Global-Migrate.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA K3 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '218-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:43:37', '2014-03-07 14:43:37', '', 218, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/218-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(445, 1, '2014-03-07 14:44:59', '2014-03-07 14:44:59', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">If your company is transferring you to a location in the United States, you’ll need an L-1 Visa. This visa is designed for intracompany transfers and can allow you to work for your employer in a managerial or other specialised position.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo find out if the L-1 visa is right for you, and to get help with your application, speak to one of Global-Migrate’s qualified immigration advisors today.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn general, your company needs to be doing business in the United States as well as another country, and intend to continue doing so. As an employee, you need to have been working for such a qualifying company for one continuous year within the three years prior to relocating to the US.\r\n\r\n\r\nLike other non-immigrant visas, you will be limited to a certain amount of time in the US. However, with an L-1 visa you will be able to bring certain family members with you. To find out which family members can travel with you, and what limits they will have on their stay, call Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\n\r\nAnother difference between the L-1 visa and some other non-immigrant visas is that you will not be required to maintain a foreign residence while you are in the US. You will also be able to apply for permanent residency, meaning you’ll be able to remain in the US even after the period of your L-1 visa is up.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe benefits of relocating to the US through an L-1 visa are great. It can allow you to migrate while keeping your existing job, and lacks many of the limitations of other employer-based visas. To find out more about whether the L-1 visa is right for you, take Global-Migrate’s free initial visa assessment today.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur qualified advisors have helped many people make their immigration dreams a reality. Let us help you prepare for your move to America.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"><a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'USA L1 Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '220-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:44:59', '2014-03-07 14:44:59', '', 220, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/220-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(446, 1, '2014-03-07 14:45:18', '2014-03-07 14:45:18', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n               If you want to travel to the United States, you’ll need a visa. Whether you want to visit for pleasure, travel for work, or join an American family member, you will need the correct visa. With many options available, it can be difficult to know the correct migration path for you. Global-Migrate’simmigration advisors are able to help you determine the best visa for your situation. We also offer a free visa assessment, so get in touch today.<br><br>\r\nAll of United States visas are divided into two categories: immigrant and non-immigrant. Immigrant visas, such as spouse visas, allow a foreign national to enter the US on a permanent basis. Non-immigrant visas are intended for those who are visiting on a temporary basis. These include work permits, such as the H-1B visa, as well as other working visas.<br><br>\r\nHowever, some non-immigration visas do allow dual intent. This means that they can be used as a path to permanent residency. For many wishing to move permanently to the United States, these visas are the best option. To find out what the right visa is for you, one of Global-Migrate’s qualified advisors can help.<br><br>\r\nIf you are married to an American citizen, or are engaged to one, you can join them in the US. You’ll need a K-1 Fiance or K-3 Spouse visa, both of which Global-Migrate can help you apply for.<br><br>\r\nThe US does limit how many immigrants allowed in each year, with strict caps on certain categories, so it is important that you apply for the right visa at the right time. Using an expert immigration advisor like Global-Migrate can increase your chances of success. We know what is required for each type of visa and can help you prepare the best application possible.<br><br>\r\nIf you’re ready to make your immigration dream come true, call or email Global-Migrate today.\r\n\r\n                     </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a></td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'USA Visas', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '199-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:45:18', '2014-03-07 14:45:18', '', 199, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/199-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(447, 1, '2014-03-07 14:46:58', '2014-03-07 14:46:58', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                  <td valign="top" class="normalTxt" colspan="2"><p>\r\n                  Canada is a North American country consisting of ten provinces and three territories. Located in the northern part of the continent, it extends from the Atlantic Ocean in the east to the Pacific Ocean in the west and northward into the Arctic Ocean. It is the world’s second largest country by total area. Canada’s common border with the United States to the south and northwest is the longest in the<br>\r\n<br>\r\n world.\r\n\r\nEvery year Canada attracts more than 5 million people as a tourist, student or temporary worker. People visit Canada to enjoy the many opportunities the country has to offer.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou will need to meet certain entry requirements depending on your nationality and your reasons to visit. Nationals of certain countries do not require a Visa to visit Canada.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIf you are required to apply for a visit visa to Canada, you will need to state reasons of your visit, the duration of the visit, proof of accommodation arrangements and funds to support you and your dependants for the entire stay.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThis type of visa allows you to enter Canada and stay there for up to 6 months. You are not allowed to work on this type of visa.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nHow long it takes to process your application varies depending on the visa office where you applied. Generally it takes between 19 &ndash; 49 days.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nYou may need to go for an interview with a visa officer. This will depend on the individuals application. You may also be required to take a medical examination to be allowed to enter Canada. If you do, a Canadian immigration officer will tell you and will send you instructions about what to do. A medical examination can add more than three months to the processing time of your application.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIt is always advisable to seek professional help for this type of visa as a slight error in your application or a mistake in your documents may result in your application being rejected and you will loose your application fee. Global-Migrate assists hunderds of applicants weekly with there visit visa appication to Canada.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n To get it right the first time please call us on +44 (0)207 9934762 \r\n					 </p>\r\n                   </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td align="left">  <a class="more" href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php" title="Start Your Free Visa Assessment"> </a>\r\n</td>\r\n                  <td align="right"><table width="157" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" border="0">\r\n          <tbody><tr>\r\n             <td width="10">&nbsp;</td> \r\n            <td width="20">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="36"></td>\r\n            <td width="34"></td>\r\n            <td width="41"></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n        </tbody></table></td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n              </tbody>\r\n            </table>', 'Visit Visa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '111-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 14:46:58', '2014-03-07 14:46:58', '', 111, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/111-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2014-03-07 14:48:51', '2014-03-07 14:48:51', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n              <tbody>\r\n                \r\n                <tr>\r\n                  <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="normalTxt"><p> \r\n                As one of the largest and most successful immigration consultancies in the world, our clients know they will get the service they need from Global-Migrate. We know what our clients go through during the visa process, and the stress it can cause. This is why we pride ourselves on our understanding and personal commitment to getting successful visa applications for our clients.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Saving time and money</strong><br /><br />\r\nIn addition to offering value for money, we save our clients’ time. By working with Global-Migrate, they don’t need to research all the details of immigration law. Instead, they are guided through the process by our trained immigration advisors.<br /><br />\r\nThey also save money by not having their application refused. An unsuccessful visa application can cost you money and can cause trouble in any future applications.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>High success rate</strong><br /><br />\r\nWe are committed to having great results. By offering a free visa assessment before we start working with any client, we only continue on cases we believe will be successful. We don’t want to put you through the cost and trouble of a visa application if we don’t think you’ll be successful.<br /><br />\r\nThis is part of our commitment to our clients. We feel that our reputation is built on our results.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Dedicated support</strong><br /><br />\r\nOur advisors provide clients with unlimited email support throughout the process. They can take your call to help with any question you might have, too. All of our advisors are highly trained and keep up to date with the ever-changing immigration rules.<br /><br />\r\nUnlike doing the visa application on your own, working