(496, 1, '2014-04-24 11:13:30', '2014-04-24 11:13:30', '<img alt="" src="http://www.canadim.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Expression-of-Interest-Web-700x300.jpg" />\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Canada Wants You !! Get a Head Start !!!</strong>\r\n\r\nFantastic news for anyone who has been thinking of Migrating to Canada for some time but have not been able to due to the very hard Canadian Immigration Rules. The immigration board of Canada has announced that the Federal Skill Visa will reopen for new applications in May 2014.Canada is one of the most popular destinations for immigrants. With its ever growing economy and job market, immigrants from the UK, Ireland, South East Asia and Africa choose to Emigrate to Canada.\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate can help you fulfill your dream as we hire a team of Canadian experts who enjoy a high success rate. <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.global-migrate.com/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></span> now for a free assessment.\r\n\r\nFederal Skilled Workers are chosen to become permanent residents based on their ability to prosper in Canada. The assessment is based on six attributes, including language, education, work experience, etc.\r\n\r\nCanada has always had 24 occupations on their skilled shortage list, however, this year they have introduced 26 more occupations making it a very attractive shortage list of 50 occupations.\r\n\r\nNurses can now migrate to Canada again and so is Immigration for Health care managers to Canada an option. Engineers, Construction Managers, IT professionals, PR Managers are some of the occupations on this exhaustive list.\r\n\r\nThe FSW program is more attractive than it has ever been. The cap has increased from just 5,000 applications a year to 25,000 this year. However the cap per application is still 1000 from all around the world, therefore, it is strongly advised that you contact us immediately to get a head start on your application and submit in time to be accepted within the 1000 application cap.\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate''s experts have welcomed the long awaited news and will be delighted to get you a head start before the occupation caps are reached. To determine your eligibility take the free online assessment below or call us 02079934762 to speak to an expert today.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left"></td>\r\n<td align="right">\r\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="10"></td>\r\n<td width="20"></td>\r\n<td width="36"></td>\r\n<td width="34"></td>\r\n<td width="41"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'The New Federal Skilled Program', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'the-new-federal-skilled-program', '', '', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '2014-11-14 16:20:39', '', 0, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/?page_id=496', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(497, 1, '2014-04-24 11:06:10', '2014-04-24 11:06:10', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="normalTxt" colspan="2" valign="top">Canada has a lot to offer, with a diverse population, wide variety of jobs, and unparalleled natural beauty. If you’re thinking about moving to Canada, you might be overwhelmed by all the types of visa available, though.\nGlobal-Migrate is an experienced immigration advisor, and we have helped many people figure out how to make their Canada immigration dream a reality. If you want to get started now, get in touch for your free visa assessment today.\n<h4>Working in Canada</h4>\nIf you want to migrate to Canada for work, there are several different visas available. One of the most popular Canadian visas is the Federal Skilled Worker visa. This points-based visa gives you permanent residency and the freedom to work in Canada. You can also apply for a work permit, which will allow you to work for a specific employer in Canada.\nGlobal-Migrate can help you apply for any Canadian working visa, and can help you determine which visa is right for you. Get in touch with us today to begin your application. We work closely with employers in Canada and can also help you find a position for a work permit.\n<h4>Studying in Canada</h4>\nCanada is home to many great universities, and is a popular destination for education. If you are planning to attend a Canadian educational institution, we can help you prepare your visa application. If you’re looking to change from a student visa to a different category, get in touch with Global-Migrate’s trained immigration consultants for advice and help with your application.\n<h4>Family in Canada</h4>\nAnother popular visa category is the Canadian family visas. These allow the spouse, parents, and children of Canadian nationals to join them in Canada. Depending on what relationship you have with the Canadian national, you’ll need to provide different information and proof. Global-Migrate has helped many people join their family in Canada, and we can help you, too.\nCanada offers these and many other ways to live in the country. We offer a free initial assessment to determine the best visa option for your individual case. Call Global-Migrate today to take the first step in making your Canada immigration dream a reality!</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="left"></td>\n<td align="right">\n<table width="157" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="10"></td>\n<td width="20"></td>\n<td width="36"></td>\n<td width="34"></td>\n<td width="41"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Canada Immigration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '101-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-24 11:06:10', '2014-04-24 11:06:10', '', 101, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/101-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
