steps that you need to take and various eligibility criteria you need to meet. If you are in a skilled occupation than we can certainly help.\r\n\r\nTo be eligible for NZ Skilled category you must:\r\n\r\n- Be under the age of 56 years\r\n- Meet the health, character and English language requirements\r\n- Be able to score the threshold of 100 points in the Points System to register an Expression of Interest.\r\n\r\nIf successful you will be eligible for a Residence Visa allowing you to enter NewZealand. and live and work there without any restrictions.\r\n\r\nTo make sure your application is successful, you’ll need to use the most up to date visa information. Global-Migrate’s expert advisers are on top of all changes to Newzealand visa rules, and can help figure out the right category for you. Before you apply on your own, get in touch for a free visa assessment and find out how we can help you.\r\n\r\nGlobal-Migrate has a very high success rate for Newzealand visa applications, and can help ensure that your visa application is not rejected. Whatever stage you’re at in your visa application, our visa experts can provide assistance.\r\n\r\nFill out our quick assessment below to find out everything about NewZealand immigration and visas now.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.global-migrate.com/free-assessment.php"><img alt="" src="https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRO6kQhvIan6tX1spTEZMCK8ku974xaJQ6fjOThwCKB9FwDluIW8A" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'NewZealand Skilled Immigration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '517-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-18 12:07:43', '2014-11-18 12:07:43', '', 517, 'http://www.global-migrate.com/517-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
